#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _NoiseTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_COLOR0;
in highp vec3 vs_NORMAL0;
in highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD4;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec4 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
bool u_xlatb0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
int u_xlati1;
bvec2 u_xlatb1;
mediump float u_xlat16_2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_7;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_10;
vec2 u_xlat11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
mediump float u_xlat16_15;
vec2 u_xlat22;
mediump float u_xlat16_22;
bool u_xlatb22;
bvec2 u_xlatb23;
float u_xlat33;
bool u_xlatb33;
bool u_xlatb34;
float u_xlat42;
void main()
{
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV1));
#else
    u_xlatb0 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV1);
#endif
    u_xlat11.xy = _Time.yy * vec2(_MainUSpeed, _MainVSpeed);
    u_xlat11.xy = fract(u_xlat11.xy);
    u_xlat0.xy = (bool(u_xlatb0)) ? vs_TEXCOORD1.xy : u_xlat11.xy;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb22 = !!(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV3Main));
#else
    u_xlatb22 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV3Main);
#endif
    u_xlat22.xy = (bool(u_xlatb22)) ? vs_TEXCOORD3.xy : vs_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat22.xy = u_xlat22.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy + u_xlat22.xy;
    u_xlat22.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _NoiseTex_ST.xy + _NoiseTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat1.xy = _Time.yy * vec2(_NoiseUSpeed, _NoiseVSpeed);
    u_xlat1.xy = fract(u_xlat1.xy);
    u_xlat22.xy = u_xlat22.xy + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat22.xy;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.xy = min(max(u_xlat1.xy, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.xy = clamp(u_xlat1.xy, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.xy = (-u_xlat22.xy) + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat22.xy = vec2(vec2(_ClampUVNoise, _ClampUVNoise)) * u_xlat1.xy + u_xlat22.xy;
    u_xlat16_22 = texture(_NoiseTex, u_xlat22.xy).x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb33 = !!(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV1Noise));
#else
    u_xlatb33 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV1Noise);
#endif
    u_xlat33 = (u_xlatb33) ? vs_TEXCOORD1.w : _NoiseIntensity;
    u_xlat0.xy = vec2(u_xlat16_22) * vec2(u_xlat33) + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat22.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat22.xy = min(max(u_xlat22.xy, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat22.xy = clamp(u_xlat22.xy, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat22.xy = (-u_xlat0.xy) + u_xlat22.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = vec2(_ClampUVMainX, _ClampUVMainY) * u_xlat22.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, u_xlat0.xy);
    u_xlatb1.xy = notEqual(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0), vec4(_RAlpha, _IF_ADD_MODE, _RAlpha, _RAlpha)).xy;
    u_xlat16_2 = (u_xlatb1.x) ? u_xlat16_0.x : u_xlat16_0.w;
    u_xlat16_3 = _ColorBlack * vec4(_EmissionBlack);
    u_xlat16_4 = _ColorLight * vec4(_EmissionLight);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb33 = !!(0.5<_UseThreeColor);
#else
    u_xlatb33 = 0.5<_UseThreeColor;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb33){
        u_xlat16_5 = _ColorMiddle * vec4(_EmissionMiddle);
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = min(max(u_xlat16_6.xyz, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = clamp(u_xlat16_6.xyz, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_6.w = u_xlat16_2 + u_xlat16_2;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_6.w = min(max(u_xlat16_6.w, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_6.w = clamp(u_xlat16_6.w, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_7 = _ColorMiddle * vec4(_EmissionMiddle) + (-u_xlat16_3);
        u_xlat16_6 = u_xlat16_6 * u_xlat16_7 + u_xlat16_3;
        u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + vec3(-0.5, -0.5, -0.5);
        u_xlat16_7.w = u_xlat16_2 + -0.5;
        u_xlat16_7 = u_xlat16_7 + u_xlat16_7;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_7 = min(max(u_xlat16_7, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_7 = clamp(u_xlat16_7, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_8 = _ColorLight * vec4(_EmissionLight) + (-u_xlat16_5);
        u_xlat16_5 = u_xlat16_7 * u_xlat16_8 + u_xlat16_5;
        u_xlat16_5 = (-u_xlat16_6) + u_xlat16_5;
        u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
        u_xlat16_7.w = u_xlat16_2 * u_xlat16_5.w;
        u_xlat16_5 = u_xlat16_6 + u_xlat16_7;
    } else {
        u_xlat16_6 = _ColorLight * vec4(_EmissionLight) + (-u_xlat16_3);
        u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
        u_xlat16_7.w = u_xlat16_2 * u_xlat16_6.w;
        u_xlat16_5 = _ColorBlack * vec4(_EmissionBlack) + u_xlat16_7;
    }
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb33 = !!(unity_WorldTransformParams.w<0.0);
#else
    u_xlatb33 = unity_WorldTransformParams.w<0.0;
#endif
    u_xlat16_10 = (uint((gl_FrontFacing ? 0xffffffffu : uint(0))) != uint(0)) ? u_xlat16_3 : u_xlat16_4;
    u_xlat16_4 = (uint((gl_FrontFacing ? 0xffffffffu : uint(0))) != uint(0)) ? u_xlat16_4 : u_xlat16_3;
    u_xlat16_3 = u_xlat16_10;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.w = u_xlat16_2 * u_xlat16_4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.w = u_xlat16_2 * u_xlat16_3.w;
    u_xlat16_0 = (bool(u_xlatb33)) ? u_xlat16_6 : u_xlat16_4;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb1.x = !!(_CullMode<0.5);
#else
    u_xlatb1.x = _CullMode<0.5;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb23.x = !!(0.5<_TwoFace);
#else
    u_xlatb23.x = 0.5<_TwoFace;
#endif
    u_xlatb1.x = u_xlatb1.x && u_xlatb23.x;
    u_xlati1 = u_xlatb1.x ? 1 : int(0);
    u_xlat16_0 = (int(u_xlati1) != 0) ? u_xlat16_0 : u_xlat16_5;
    u_xlat1.x = _Time.y * _ColorFrequency;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.00318471342;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb23.x = !!(u_xlat1.x>=(-u_xlat1.x));
#else
    u_xlatb23.x = u_xlat1.x>=(-u_xlat1.x);
#endif
    u_xlat1.x = fract(abs(u_xlat1.x));
    u_xlat1.x = (u_xlatb23.x) ? u_xlat1.x : (-u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 314.0;
    u_xlat1.x = sin(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlatb23.xy = notEqual(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0), vec4(_IsLerpColor, _NoVertexColor, _IsLerpColor, _NoVertexColor)).xy;
    u_xlat3 = (-u_xlat16_0) + _ColorLerp;
    u_xlat3 = abs(u_xlat1.xxxx) * u_xlat3 + u_xlat16_0;
    u_xlat0 = (u_xlatb23.x) ? u_xlat3 : u_xlat16_0;
    u_xlat16_3 = (u_xlatb23.y) ? vec4(1.0, 1.0, 1.0, 1.0) : vs_COLOR0;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(vs_NORMAL0.xyz, vs_NORMAL0.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat1.xxx * vs_NORMAL0.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat42 = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat42 = inversesqrt(u_xlat42);
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat42) * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat1.xzw, u_xlat9.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.x = min(max(u_xlat1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat1.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_13.x = max(_FresnelPower, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.x = log2(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat1.x = exp2(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * _FresnelColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * vec3(vec3(_FresnelEmission, _FresnelEmission, _FresnelEmission));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat0.w * u_xlat16_2;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat1.x * _FresnelEmission;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_15 = _FresnelColor.w * _InvertFresnel + (-u_xlat16_2);
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_15 + u_xlat16_2;
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat0.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_2 * _Alpha;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_3.w * u_xlat16_2;
    u_xlat16_13.x = (u_xlatb1.y) ? u_xlat16_2 : 1.0;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xzw * u_xlat16_13.xxx;
    u_xlat16_13.x = _SrcBlendFactor * _DstBlendFactor;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb34 = !!(u_xlat16_13.x==1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb34 = u_xlat16_13.x==1.0;
#endif
    SV_Target0.w = (u_xlatb34) ? 0.00100000005 : u_xlat16_2;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}
SubProgram "gles " {
Local Keywords { "_FRESNEL_ON" "_MASK_ON" }
"// hash: 86e71d948a5ff504
#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
uniform 	mediump float _Zoffset;
uniform 	mediump float _RotateUV;
uniform 	mediump float _RotateUVAngle;
uniform 	mediump float _CylinderUV;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _CenterOffset;
uniform 	mediump float _Axis;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TEXCOORD1;
attribute highp vec4 in_TEXCOORD2;
attribute mediump vec4 in_COLOR0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TEXCOORD3;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD2;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_COLOR0;
varying highp vec3 vs_NORMAL0;
varying highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD4;
vec3 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
bool u_xlatb2;
vec2 u_xlat3;
vec2 u_xlat4;
vec2 u_xlat7;
bool u_xlatb7;
float u_xlat12;
bool u_xlatb12;
bool u_xlatb13;
float u_xlat15;
bool u_xlatb15;
float u_xlat17;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    u_xlatb15 = 0.5<_RotateUV;
    if(u_xlatb15){
        u_xlat15 = _RotateUVAngle * 0.0174532924;
        u_xlat2.x = sin(u_xlat15);
        u_xlat3.x = cos(u_xlat15);
        u_xlat7.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.yx + vec2(-0.5, -0.5);
        u_xlat2.xw = u_xlat7.xy * u_xlat2.xx;
        u_xlat15 = u_xlat3.x * u_xlat7.y + (-u_xlat2.x);
        u_xlat4.x = u_xlat15 + 0.5;
        u_xlat15 = u_xlat3.x * u_xlat7.x + u_xlat2.w;
        u_xlat4.y = u_xlat15 + 0.5;
    } else {
        u_xlat4.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    }
    u_xlat2.xyz = in_POSITION0.yzx + _CenterOffset.yzx;
    u_xlatb15 = _Axis<1.0;
    if(u_xlatb15){
        u_xlat3.y = u_xlat2.z;
    } else {
        u_xlatb15 = _Axis==1.0;
        u_xlat3.xy = (bool(u_xlatb15)) ? u_xlat2.yx : u_xlat2.xy;
        u_xlat2.w = u_xlat3.x;
        u_xlat2.xy = u_xlat2.zw;
    }
    u_xlat15 = min(abs(u_xlat2.x), abs(u_xlat2.y));
    u_xlat12 = max(abs(u_xlat2.x), abs(u_xlat2.y));
    u_xlat12 = float(1.0) / u_xlat12;
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat15 * u_xlat12;
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat15 * u_xlat15;
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat12 * 0.0208350997 + -0.0851330012;
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat12 * u_xlat17 + 0.180141002;
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat12 * u_xlat17 + -0.330299497;
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat12 * u_xlat17 + 0.999866009;
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat15 * u_xlat12;
    u_xlatb13 = abs(u_xlat2.x)<abs(u_xlat2.y);
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat17 * -2.0 + 1.57079637;
    u_xlat17 = u_xlatb13 ? u_xlat17 : float(0.0);
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat15 * u_xlat12 + u_xlat17;
    u_xlatb12 = u_xlat2.x<(-u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat12 = u_xlatb12 ? -3.14159274 : float(0.0);
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat15 + u_xlat12;
    u_xlat12 = min(u_xlat2.x, u_xlat2.y);
    u_xlat2.x = max(u_xlat2.x, u_xlat2.y);
    u_xlatb7 = u_xlat12<(-u_xlat12);
    u_xlatb2 = u_xlat2.x>=(-u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlatb2 = u_xlatb2 && u_xlatb7;
    u_xlat15 = (u_xlatb2) ? (-u_xlat15) : u_xlat15;
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat15 * 0.159154937 + 0.5;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat15 + _CenterOffset.w;
    u_xlatb15 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_CylinderUV);
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = (bool(u_xlatb15)) ? u_xlat3.xy : u_xlat4.xy;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    vs_NORMAL0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = _Zoffset / u_xlat1.w;
    gl_Position.z = (-u_xlat15) + u_xlat1.z;
    gl_Position.xyw = u_xlat1.xyw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = vec2(0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = in_TEXCOORD1;
    vs_TEXCOORD2 = in_TEXCOORD2;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = in_TEXCOORD3;
    vs_COLOR0 = in_COLOR0;
    vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    return;
}

#endif
#ifdef FRAGMENT
#version 100

#ifdef GL_FRAGMENT_PRECISION_HIGH
    precision highp float;
#else
    precision mediump float;
#endif
precision highp int;

uniform 	mediump float _EmissionMiddle;

uniform 	mediump float _ClampUVMainY;

uniform 	mediump float _ClampUVMaskY;
uniform 	mediump float _UseUV2Mask;

uniform lowp sampler2D _MaskTex;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD2;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_COLOR0;
varying highp vec3 vs_NORMAL0;
varying highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD4;
#define SV_Target0 gl_FragData[0]
vec4 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
lowp vec4 u_xlat10_0;
bool u_xlatb0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
int u_xlati1;
bvec2 u_xlatb1;
mediump float u_xlat16_2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_7;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
lowp float u_xlat10_9;
bvec2 u_xlatb9;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_10;
vec2 u_xlat11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
mediump float u_xlat16_15;
vec3 u_xlat20;
vec2 u_xlat22;
bool u_xlatb22;
bvec2 u_xlatb23;
mediump float u_xlat16_24;
vec2 u_xlat31;
bool u_xlatb33;
bool u_xlatb34;
float u_xlat42;
void main()
{
    u_xlatb0 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV1);
    u_xlat11.xy = _Time.yy * vec2(_MainUSpeed, _MainVSpeed);
    u_xlat11.xy = fract(u_xlat11.xy);
    u_xlat0.xy = (bool(u_xlatb0)) ? vs_TEXCOORD1.xy : u_xlat11.xy;
    u_xlatb22 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV3Main);
    u_xlat22.xy = (bool(u_xlatb22)) ? vs_TEXCOORD3.xy : vs_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat22.xy = u_xlat22.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy + u_xlat22.xy;
    u_xlat22.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat22.xy = clamp(u_xlat22.xy, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat22.xy = (-u_xlat0.xy) + u_xlat22.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = vec2(_ClampUVMainX, _ClampUVMainY) * u_xlat22.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat10_0 = texture2D(_MainTex, u_xlat0.xy);
    u_xlatb1.xy = notEqual(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0), vec4(_RAlpha, _IF_ADD_MODE, _RAlpha, _RAlpha)).xy;
    u_xlat16_2 = (u_xlatb1.x) ? u_xlat10_0.x : u_xlat10_0.w;
    u_xlat16_3 = _ColorBlack * vec4(_EmissionBlack);
    u_xlat16_4 = _ColorLight * vec4(_EmissionLight);
    u_xlatb33 = 0.5<_UseThreeColor;
    if(u_xlatb33){
        u_xlat16_5 = _ColorMiddle * vec4(_EmissionMiddle);
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz + u_xlat10_0.xyz;
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = clamp(u_xlat16_6.xyz, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_6.w = u_xlat16_2 + u_xlat16_2;
        u_xlat16_6.w = clamp(u_xlat16_6.w, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_7 = _ColorMiddle * vec4(_EmissionMiddle) + (-u_xlat16_3);
        u_xlat16_6 = u_xlat16_6 * u_xlat16_7 + u_xlat16_3;
        u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz + vec3(-0.5, -0.5, -0.5);
        u_xlat16_7.w = u_xlat16_2 + -0.5;
        u_xlat16_7 = u_xlat16_7 + u_xlat16_7;
        u_xlat16_7 = clamp(u_xlat16_7, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_8 = _ColorLight * vec4(_EmissionLight) + (-u_xlat16_5);
        u_xlat16_5 = u_xlat16_7 * u_xlat16_8 + u_xlat16_5;
        u_xlat16_5 = (-u_xlat16_6) + u_xlat16_5;
        u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
        u_xlat16_7.w = u_xlat16_2 * u_xlat16_5.w;
        u_xlat16_5 = u_xlat16_6 + u_xlat16_7;
    } else {
        u_xlat16_6 = _ColorLight * vec4(_EmissionLight) + (-u_xlat16_3);
        u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
        u_xlat16_7.w = u_xlat16_2 * u_xlat16_6.w;
        u_xlat16_5 = _ColorBlack * vec4(_EmissionBlack) + u_xlat16_7;
    }
    u_xlatb33 = unity_WorldTransformParams.w<0.0;
    u_xlat16_10 = (int((gl_FrontFacing ? 1 : 0)) != 0) ? u_xlat16_3 : u_xlat16_4;
    u_xlat16_4 = (int((gl_FrontFacing ? 1 : 0)) != 0) ? u_xlat16_4 : u_xlat16_3;
    u_xlat16_3 = u_xlat16_10;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.w = u_xlat16_2 * u_xlat16_4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.w = u_xlat16_2 * u_xlat16_3.w;
    u_xlat16_0 = (bool(u_xlatb33)) ? u_xlat16_6 : u_xlat16_4;
    u_xlatb1.x = _CullMode<0.5;
    u_xlatb23.x = 0.5<_TwoFace;
    u_xlatb1.x = u_xlatb1.x && u_xlatb23.x;
    u_xlati1 = u_xlatb1.x ? 1 : int(0);
    u_xlat16_0 = (int(u_xlati1) != 0) ? u_xlat16_0 : u_xlat16_5;
    u_xlat1.x = _Time.y * _ColorFrequency;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.00318471342;
    u_xlatb23.x = u_xlat1.x>=(-u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.x = fract(abs(u_xlat1.x));
    u_xlat1.x = (u_xlatb23.x) ? u_xlat1.x : (-u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 314.0;
    u_xlat1.x = sin(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlatb23.xy = notEqual(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0), vec4(_IsLerpColor, _NoVertexColor, _IsLerpColor, _NoVertexColor)).xy;
    u_xlat3 = (-u_xlat16_0) + _ColorLerp;
    u_xlat3 = abs(u_xlat1.xxxx) * u_xlat3 + u_xlat16_0;
    u_xlat0 = (u_xlatb23.x) ? u_xlat3 : u_xlat16_0;
    u_xlat16_3 = (u_xlatb23.y) ? vec4(1.0, 1.0, 1.0, 1.0) : vs_COLOR0;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(vs_NORMAL0.xyz, vs_NORMAL0.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat1.xxx * vs_NORMAL0.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat42 = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat42 = inversesqrt(u_xlat42);
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat42) * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat1.xzw, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat1.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_13.x = max(_FresnelPower, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.x = log2(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat1.x = exp2(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * _FresnelColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * vec3(vec3(_FresnelEmission, _FresnelEmission, _FresnelEmission));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat0.w * u_xlat16_2;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat1.x * _FresnelEmission;
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_15 = _FresnelColor.w * _InvertFresnel + (-u_xlat16_2);
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_15 + u_xlat16_2;
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat0.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlatb9.xy = notEqual(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0), vec4(_UseUV2Mask, _UseUV3Mask, _UseUV2Mask, _UseUV2Mask)).xy;
    u_xlat31.xy = _Time.yy * vec2(_MaskUSpeed, _MaskVSpeed);
    u_xlat31.xy = fract(u_xlat31.xy);
    u_xlat9.xz = (u_xlatb9.x) ? vs_TEXCOORD2.xy : u_xlat31.xy;
    u_xlat20.xz = (u_xlatb9.y) ? vs_TEXCOORD3.xy : vs_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat20.xz = u_xlat20.xz * _MaskTex_ST.xy + _MaskTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xz + u_xlat20.xz;
    u_xlat31.xy = u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat31.xy = clamp(u_xlat31.xy, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat31.xy = (-u_xlat9.xy) + u_xlat31.xy;
    u_xlat9.xy = vec2(_ClampUVMaskX, _ClampUVMaskY) * u_xlat31.xy + u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat10_9 = texture2D(_MaskTex, u_xlat9.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat10_9 + (-_MaskIntensity);
    u_xlat16_13.x = clamp(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_24 = (-_MaskIntensity) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_24 = _MaskFeatheredIntensity * u_xlat16_24 + 9.99999975e-05;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x / u_xlat16_24;
    u_xlat16_13.x = clamp(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_2;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_2 * _Alpha;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_3.w * u_xlat16_2;
    u_xlat16_13.x = (u_xlatb1.y) ? u_xlat16_2 : 1.0;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xzw * u_xlat16_13.xxx;
    u_xlat16_13.x = _SrcBlendFactor * _DstBlendFactor;
    u_xlatb34 = u_xlat16_13.x==1.0;
    SV_Target0.w = (u_xlatb34) ? 0.00100000005 : u_xlat16_2;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz;
    return;
}

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _UseUV3Main;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _FlipAnim;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _flipCycle;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _flipOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _NoiseTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _NoiseUSpeed;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _NoiseVSpeed;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _NoiseIntensity;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ClampUVNoise;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AffectDissolveMask;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _UseUV1Noise;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MaskTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MaskUSpeed;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MaskVSpeed;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MaskIntensity;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MaskFeatheredIntensity;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ClampUVMaskX;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ClampUVMaskY;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _UseUV2Mask;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _UseUV3Mask;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _DissolveTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _DissolveUSpeed;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _DissolveVSpeed;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _DissolveEdge;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _DissolveRange;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _UseUV1Dissolve;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _ClampUVDissolve;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _ColorEdgeWidth;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _EdgeColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _EdgeEmission;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _UseUV2DissolveOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _FresnelColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _FresnelPower;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _FresnelEmission;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _InvertFresnel;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _DisturbVector;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _DisturbTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DisturbUSpeed;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DisturbVSpeed;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DisturbAnimToggle;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _VertAmplitude;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
in highp vec4 in_TEXCOORD1;
in highp vec4 in_TEXCOORD2;
in mediump vec4 in_COLOR0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TEXCOORD3;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_COLOR0;
out highp vec3 vs_NORMAL0;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD4;
vec3 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
bool u_xlatb2;
vec2 u_xlat3;
vec2 u_xlat4;
vec2 u_xlat7;
bool u_xlatb7;
float u_xlat12;
bool u_xlatb12;
bool u_xlatb13;
float u_xlat15;
bool u_xlatb15;
float u_xlat17;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb15 = !!(0.5<_RotateUV);
#else
    u_xlatb15 = 0.5<_RotateUV;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb15){
        u_xlat15 = _RotateUVAngle * 0.0174532924;
        u_xlat2.x = sin(u_xlat15);
        u_xlat3.x = cos(u_xlat15);
        u_xlat7.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.yx + vec2(-0.5, -0.5);
        u_xlat2.xw = u_xlat7.xy * u_xlat2.xx;
        u_xlat15 = u_xlat3.x * u_xlat7.y + (-u_xlat2.x);
        u_xlat4.x = u_xlat15 + 0.5;
        u_xlat15 = u_xlat3.x * u_xlat7.x + u_xlat2.w;
        u_xlat4.y = u_xlat15 + 0.5;
    } else {
        u_xlat4.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    }
    u_xlat2.xyz = in_POSITION0.yzx + _CenterOffset.yzx;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb15 = !!(_Axis<1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb15 = _Axis<1.0;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb15){
        u_xlat3.y = u_xlat2.z;
    } else {
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb15 = !!(_Axis==1.0);
#else
        u_xlatb15 = _Axis==1.0;
#endif
        u_xlat3.xy = (bool(u_xlatb15)) ? u_xlat2.yx : u_xlat2.xy;
        u_xlat2.w = u_xlat3.x;
        u_xlat2.xy = u_xlat2.zw;
    }
    u_xlat15 = min(abs(u_xlat2.x), abs(u_xlat2.y));
    u_xlat12 = max(abs(u_xlat2.x), abs(u_xlat2.y));
    u_xlat12 = float(1.0) / u_xlat12;
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat15 * u_xlat12;
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat15 * u_xlat15;
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat12 * 0.0208350997 + -0.0851330012;
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat12 * u_xlat17 + 0.180141002;
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat12 * u_xlat17 + -0.330299497;
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat12 * u_xlat17 + 0.999866009;
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat15 * u_xlat12;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb13 = !!(abs(u_xlat2.x)<abs(u_xlat2.y));
#else
    u_xlatb13 = abs(u_xlat2.x)<abs(u_xlat2.y);
#endif
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat17 * -2.0 + 1.57079637;
    u_xlat17 = u_xlatb13 ? u_xlat17 : float(0.0);
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat15 * u_xlat12 + u_xlat17;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb12 = !!(u_xlat2.x<(-u_xlat2.x));
#else
    u_xlatb12 = u_xlat2.x<(-u_xlat2.x);
#endif
    u_xlat12 = u_xlatb12 ? -3.14159274 : float(0.0);
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat15 + u_xlat12;
    u_xlat12 = min(u_xlat2.x, u_xlat2.y);
    u_xlat2.x = max(u_xlat2.x, u_xlat2.y);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb7 = !!(u_xlat12<(-u_xlat12));
#else
    u_xlatb7 = u_xlat12<(-u_xlat12);
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb2 = !!(u_xlat2.x>=(-u_xlat2.x));
#else
    u_xlatb2 = u_xlat2.x>=(-u_xlat2.x);
#endif
    u_xlatb2 = u_xlatb2 && u_xlatb7;
    u_xlat15 = (u_xlatb2) ? (-u_xlat15) : u_xlat15;
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat15 * 0.159154937 + 0.5;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat15 + _CenterOffset.w;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb15 = !!(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_CylinderUV));
#else
    u_xlatb15 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_CylinderUV);
#endif
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = (bool(u_xlatb15)) ? u_xlat3.xy : u_xlat4.xy;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    vs_NORMAL0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = _Zoffset / u_xlat1.w;
    gl_Position.z = (-u_xlat15) + u_xlat1.z;
    gl_Position.xyw = u_xlat1.xyw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = vec2(0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = in_TEXCOORD1;
    vs_TEXCOORD2 = in_TEXCOORD2;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = in_TEXCOORD3;
    vs_COLOR0 = in_COLOR0;
    vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    return;
}

#endif

#endif
uniform 	vec4 _Time;
uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(0) uniform UnityPerDraw {

};

#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(1) uniform UnityPerMaterial {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ClipValue;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _ColorLight;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _EmissionLight;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _ColorBlack;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _EmissionBlack;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _UseThreeColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _ColorMiddle;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _EmissionMiddle;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Alpha;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Zoffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _UseUV1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MainUSpeed;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MainVSpeed;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _NoVertexColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _IsLerpColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RowNum;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ColumNum;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _FlipSpeed;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _ColorLerp;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ColorFrequency;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ClampUVMainX;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ClampUVMainY;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RotateUV;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RotateUVAngle;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RAlpha;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _IF_ADD_MODE;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SrcBlendFactor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DstBlendFactor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _CylinderUV;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _CenterOffset;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MaskFeatheredIntensity;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ClampUVMaskX;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ClampUVMaskY;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _UseUV2Mask;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _UseUV3Mask;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _DissolveTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _DissolveUSpeed;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _DissolveVSpeed;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _DissolveEdge;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _DissolveRange;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _UseUV1Dissolve;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _ClampUVDissolve;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _ColorEdgeWidth;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _EdgeColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _EdgeEmission;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _UseUV2DissolveOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _FresnelColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _FresnelPower;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _FresnelEmission;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _InvertFresnel;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _DisturbVector;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _DisturbTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DisturbUSpeed;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DisturbVSpeed;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DisturbAnimToggle;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _VertAmplitude;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MaskTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD2;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_COLOR0;
in highp vec3 vs_NORMAL0;
in highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD4;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec4 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
bool u_xlatb0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
int u_xlati1;
bvec2 u_xlatb1;
mediump float u_xlat16_2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_7;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
mediump float u_xlat16_9;
bvec2 u_xlatb9;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_10;
vec2 u_xlat11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
mediump float u_xlat16_15;
vec3 u_xlat20;
vec2 u_xlat22;
bool u_xlatb22;
bvec2 u_xlatb23;
mediump float u_xlat16_24;
vec2 u_xlat31;
bool u_xlatb33;
bool u_xlatb34;
float u_xlat42;
void main()
{
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV1));
#else
    u_xlatb0 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV1);
#endif
    u_xlat11.xy = _Time.yy * vec2(_MainUSpeed, _MainVSpeed);
    u_xlat11.xy = fract(u_xlat11.xy);
    u_xlat0.xy = (bool(u_xlatb0)) ? vs_TEXCOORD1.xy : u_xlat11.xy;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb22 = !!(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV3Main));
#else
    u_xlatb22 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV3Main);
#endif
    u_xlat22.xy = (bool(u_xlatb22)) ? vs_TEXCOORD3.xy : vs_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat22.xy = u_xlat22.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy + u_xlat22.xy;
    u_xlat22.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat22.xy = min(max(u_xlat22.xy, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat22.xy = clamp(u_xlat22.xy, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat22.xy = (-u_xlat0.xy) + u_xlat22.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = vec2(_ClampUVMainX, _ClampUVMainY) * u_xlat22.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, u_xlat0.xy);
    u_xlatb1.xy = notEqual(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0), vec4(_RAlpha, _IF_ADD_MODE, _RAlpha, _RAlpha)).xy;
    u_xlat16_2 = (u_xlatb1.x) ? u_xlat16_0.x : u_xlat16_0.w;
    u_xlat16_3 = _ColorBlack * vec4(_EmissionBlack);
    u_xlat16_4 = _ColorLight * vec4(_EmissionLight);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb33 = !!(0.5<_UseThreeColor);
#else
    u_xlatb33 = 0.5<_UseThreeColor;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb33){
        u_xlat16_5 = _ColorMiddle * vec4(_EmissionMiddle);
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = min(max(u_xlat16_6.xyz, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = clamp(u_xlat16_6.xyz, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_6.w = u_xlat16_2 + u_xlat16_2;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_6.w = min(max(u_xlat16_6.w, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_6.w = clamp(u_xlat16_6.w, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_7 = _ColorMiddle * vec4(_EmissionMiddle) + (-u_xlat16_3);
        u_xlat16_6 = u_xlat16_6 * u_xlat16_7 + u_xlat16_3;
        u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + vec3(-0.5, -0.5, -0.5);
        u_xlat16_7.w = u_xlat16_2 + -0.5;
        u_xlat16_7 = u_xlat16_7 + u_xlat16_7;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_7 = min(max(u_xlat16_7, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_7 = clamp(u_xlat16_7, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_8 = _ColorLight * vec4(_EmissionLight) + (-u_xlat16_5);
        u_xlat16_5 = u_xlat16_7 * u_xlat16_8 + u_xlat16_5;
        u_xlat16_5 = (-u_xlat16_6) + u_xlat16_5;
        u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
        u_xlat16_7.w = u_xlat16_2 * u_xlat16_5.w;
        u_xlat16_5 = u_xlat16_6 + u_xlat16_7;
    } else {
        u_xlat16_6 = _ColorLight * vec4(_EmissionLight) + (-u_xlat16_3);
        u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
        u_xlat16_7.w = u_xlat16_2 * u_xlat16_6.w;
        u_xlat16_5 = _ColorBlack * vec4(_EmissionBlack) + u_xlat16_7;
    }
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb33 = !!(unity_WorldTransformParams.w<0.0);
#else
    u_xlatb33 = unity_WorldTransformParams.w<0.0;
#endif
    u_xlat16_10 = (uint((gl_FrontFacing ? 0xffffffffu : uint(0))) != uint(0)) ? u_xlat16_3 : u_xlat16_4;
    u_xlat16_4 = (uint((gl_FrontFacing ? 0xffffffffu : uint(0))) != uint(0)) ? u_xlat16_4 : u_xlat16_3;
    u_xlat16_3 = u_xlat16_10;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.w = u_xlat16_2 * u_xlat16_4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.w = u_xlat16_2 * u_xlat16_3.w;
    u_xlat16_0 = (bool(u_xlatb33)) ? u_xlat16_6 : u_xlat16_4;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb1.x = !!(_CullMode<0.5);
#else
    u_xlatb1.x = _CullMode<0.5;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb23.x = !!(0.5<_TwoFace);
#else
    u_xlatb23.x = 0.5<_TwoFace;
#endif
    u_xlatb1.x = u_xlatb1.x && u_xlatb23.x;
    u_xlati1 = u_xlatb1.x ? 1 : int(0);
    u_xlat16_0 = (int(u_xlati1) != 0) ? u_xlat16_0 : u_xlat16_5;
    u_xlat1.x = _Time.y * _ColorFrequency;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.00318471342;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb23.x = !!(u_xlat1.x>=(-u_xlat1.x));
#else
    u_xlatb23.x = u_xlat1.x>=(-u_xlat1.x);
#endif
    u_xlat1.x = fract(abs(u_xlat1.x));
    u_xlat1.x = (u_xlatb23.x) ? u_xlat1.x : (-u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 314.0;
    u_xlat1.x = sin(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlatb23.xy = notEqual(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0), vec4(_IsLerpColor, _NoVertexColor, _IsLerpColor, _NoVertexColor)).xy;
    u_xlat3 = (-u_xlat16_0) + _ColorLerp;
    u_xlat3 = abs(u_xlat1.xxxx) * u_xlat3 + u_xlat16_0;
    u_xlat0 = (u_xlatb23.x) ? u_xlat3 : u_xlat16_0;
    u_xlat16_3 = (u_xlatb23.y) ? vec4(1.0, 1.0, 1.0, 1.0) : vs_COLOR0;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(vs_NORMAL0.xyz, vs_NORMAL0.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat1.xxx * vs_NORMAL0.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat42 = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat42 = inversesqrt(u_xlat42);
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat42) * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat1.xzw, u_xlat9.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.x = min(max(u_xlat1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat1.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_13.x = max(_FresnelPower, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.x = log2(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat1.x = exp2(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * _FresnelColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * vec3(vec3(_FresnelEmission, _FresnelEmission, _FresnelEmission));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat0.w * u_xlat16_2;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat1.x * _FresnelEmission;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_15 = _FresnelColor.w * _InvertFresnel + (-u_xlat16_2);
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_15 + u_xlat16_2;
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat0.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlatb9.xy = notEqual(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0), vec4(_UseUV2Mask, _UseUV3Mask, _UseUV2Mask, _UseUV2Mask)).xy;
    u_xlat31.xy = _Time.yy * vec2(_MaskUSpeed, _MaskVSpeed);
    u_xlat31.xy = fract(u_xlat31.xy);
    u_xlat9.xz = (u_xlatb9.x) ? vs_TEXCOORD2.xy : u_xlat31.xy;
    u_xlat20.xz = (u_xlatb9.y) ? vs_TEXCOORD3.xy : vs_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat20.xz = u_xlat20.xz * _MaskTex_ST.xy + _MaskTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xz + u_xlat20.xz;
    u_xlat31.xy = u_xlat9.xy;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat31.xy = min(max(u_xlat31.xy, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat31.xy = clamp(u_xlat31.xy, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat31.xy = (-u_xlat9.xy) + u_xlat31.xy;
    u_xlat9.xy = vec2(_ClampUVMaskX, _ClampUVMaskY) * u_xlat31.xy + u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat16_9 = texture(_MaskTex, u_xlat9.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_9 + (-_MaskIntensity);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_13.x = min(max(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_13.x = clamp(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_24 = (-_MaskIntensity) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_24 = _MaskFeatheredIntensity * u_xlat16_24 + 9.99999975e-05;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x / u_xlat16_24;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_13.x = min(max(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_13.x = clamp(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_2;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_2 * _Alpha;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_3.w * u_xlat16_2;
    u_xlat16_13.x = (u_xlatb1.y) ? u_xlat16_2 : 1.0;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xzw * u_xlat16_13.xxx;
    u_xlat16_13.x = _SrcBlendFactor * _DstBlendFactor;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb34 = !!(u_xlat16_13.x==1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb34 = u_xlat16_13.x==1.0;
#endif
    SV_Target0.w = (u_xlatb34) ? 0.00100000005 : u_xlat16_2;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz;
    return;
}

    u_xlat42 = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat42 = inversesqrt(u_xlat42);
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat42) * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat1.xzw, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat1.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_13.x = max(_FresnelPower, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.x = log2(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat1.x = exp2(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * _FresnelColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * vec3(vec3(_FresnelEmission, _FresnelEmission, _FresnelEmission));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat0.w * u_xlat16_2;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat1.x * _FresnelEmission;
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_15 = _FresnelColor.w * _InvertFresnel + (-u_xlat16_2);
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_15 + u_xlat16_2;
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat0.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlatb9.xy = notEqual(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0), vec4(_UseUV2Mask, _UseUV3Mask, _UseUV2Mask, _UseUV2Mask)).xy;
    u_xlat31.xy = _Time.yy * vec2(_MaskUSpeed, _MaskVSpeed);
    u_xlat31.xy = fract(u_xlat31.xy);
    u_xlat9.xz = (u_xlatb9.x) ? vs_TEXCOORD2.xy : u_xlat31.xy;
    u_xlat20.xz = (u_xlatb9.y) ? vs_TEXCOORD3.xy : vs_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat20.xz = u_xlat20.xz * _MaskTex_ST.xy + _MaskTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xz + u_xlat20.xz;
    u_xlat31.xy = u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat31.xy = clamp(u_xlat31.xy, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat31.xy = (-u_xlat9.xy) + u_xlat31.xy;
    u_xlat9.xy = vec2(_ClampUVMaskX, _ClampUVMaskY) * u_xlat31.xy + u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat10_9 = texture2D(_MaskTex, u_xlat9.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat10_9 + (-_MaskIntensity);
    u_xlat16_13.x = clamp(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_24 = (-_MaskIntensity) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_24 = _MaskFeatheredIntensity * u_xlat16_24 + 9.99999975e-05;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x / u_xlat16_24;
    u_xlat16_13.x = clamp(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_2;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_2 * _Alpha;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_3.w * u_xlat16_2;
    u_xlat16_24 = (u_xlatb1.y) ? u_xlat16_13.x : 1.0;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xzw * vec3(u_xlat16_24);
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_2 * u_xlat16_3.w + (-_ClipValue);
    u_xlatb34 = u_xlat16_2<0.0;
    if(u_xlatb34){discard;}
    u_xlat16_2 = _SrcBlendFactor * _DstBlendFactor;
    u_xlatb34 = u_xlat16_2==1.0;
    SV_Target0.w = (u_xlatb34) ? 0.00100000005 : u_xlat16_13.x;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}

in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
in highp vec4 in_TEXCOORD1;
in highp vec4 in_TEXCOORD2;
in mediump vec4 in_COLOR0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TEXCOORD3;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_COLOR0;
out highp vec3 vs_NORMAL0;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD4;
vec3 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
bool u_xlatb2;
vec2 u_xlat3;
vec2 u_xlat4;
vec2 u_xlat7;
bool u_xlatb7;
float u_xlat12;
bool u_xlatb12;
bool u_xlatb13;
float u_xlat15;
bool u_xlatb15;
float u_xlat17;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb15 = !!(0.5<_RotateUV);
#else
    u_xlatb15 = 0.5<_RotateUV;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb15){
        u_xlat15 = _RotateUVAngle * 0.0174532924;
        u_xlat2.x = sin(u_xlat15);
        u_xlat3.x = cos(u_xlat15);
        u_xlat7.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.yx + vec2(-0.5, -0.5);
        u_xlat2.xw = u_xlat7.xy * u_xlat2.xx;
        u_xlat15 = u_xlat3.x * u_xlat7.y + (-u_xlat2.x);
        u_xlat4.x = u_xlat15 + 0.5;
        u_xlat15 = u_xlat3.x * u_xlat7.x + u_xlat2.w;
        u_xlat4.y = u_xlat15 + 0.5;
    } else {
        u_xlat4.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    }
    u_xlat2.xyz = in_POSITION0.yzx + _CenterOffset.yzx;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb15 = !!(_Axis<1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb15 = _Axis<1.0;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb15){
        u_xlat3.y = u_xlat2.z;
    } else {
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb15 = !!(_Axis==1.0);
#else
        u_xlatb15 = _Axis==1.0;
#endif
        u_xlat3.xy = (bool(u_xlatb15)) ? u_xlat2.yx : u_xlat2.xy;
        u_xlat2.w = u_xlat3.x;
        u_xlat2.xy = u_xlat2.zw;
    }
    u_xlat15 = min(abs(u_xlat2.x), abs(u_xlat2.y));
    u_xlat12 = max(abs(u_xlat2.x), abs(u_xlat2.y));
    u_xlat12 = float(1.0) / u_xlat12;
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat15 * u_xlat12;
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat15 * u_xlat15;
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat12 * 0.0208350997 + -0.0851330012;
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat12 * u_xlat17 + 0.180141002;
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat12 * u_xlat17 + -0.330299497;
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat12 * u_xlat17 + 0.999866009;
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat15 * u_xlat12;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb13 = !!(abs(u_xlat2.x)<abs(u_xlat2.y));
#else
    u_xlatb13 = abs(u_xlat2.x)<abs(u_xlat2.y);
#endif
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat17 * -2.0 + 1.57079637;
    u_xlat17 = u_xlatb13 ? u_xlat17 : float(0.0);
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat15 * u_xlat12 + u_xlat17;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb12 = !!(u_xlat2.x<(-u_xlat2.x));
#else
    u_xlatb12 = u_xlat2.x<(-u_xlat2.x);
#endif
    u_xlat12 = u_xlatb12 ? -3.14159274 : float(0.0);
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat15 + u_xlat12;
    u_xlat12 = min(u_xlat2.x, u_xlat2.y);
    u_xlat2.x = max(u_xlat2.x, u_xlat2.y);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb7 = !!(u_xlat12<(-u_xlat12));
#else
    u_xlatb7 = u_xlat12<(-u_xlat12);
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb2 = !!(u_xlat2.x>=(-u_xlat2.x));
#else
    u_xlatb2 = u_xlat2.x>=(-u_xlat2.x);
#endif
    u_xlatb2 = u_xlatb2 && u_xlatb7;
    u_xlat15 = (u_xlatb2) ? (-u_xlat15) : u_xlat15;
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat15 * 0.159154937 + 0.5;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat15 + _CenterOffset.w;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb15 = !!(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_CylinderUV));
#else
    u_xlatb15 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_CylinderUV);
#endif
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = (bool(u_xlatb15)) ? u_xlat3.xy : u_xlat4.xy;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    vs_NORMAL0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = _Zoffset / u_xlat1.w;
    gl_Position.z = (-u_xlat15) + u_xlat1.z;
    gl_Position.xyw = u_xlat1.xyw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = vec2(0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = in_TEXCOORD1;
    vs_TEXCOORD2 = in_TEXCOORD2;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = in_TEXCOORD3;
    vs_COLOR0 = in_COLOR0;
    vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    return;
}

#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MaskTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD2;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_COLOR0;
in highp vec3 vs_NORMAL0;
in highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD4;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec4 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
bool u_xlatb0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
int u_xlati1;
bvec2 u_xlatb1;
mediump float u_xlat16_2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_7;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
mediump float u_xlat16_9;
bvec2 u_xlatb9;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_10;
vec2 u_xlat11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
mediump float u_xlat16_15;
vec3 u_xlat20;
vec2 u_xlat22;
bool u_xlatb22;
bvec2 u_xlatb23;
mediump float u_xlat16_24;
vec2 u_xlat31;
bool u_xlatb33;
bool u_xlatb34;
float u_xlat42;
void main()
{
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV1));
#else
    u_xlatb0 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV1);
#endif
    u_xlat11.xy = _Time.yy * vec2(_MainUSpeed, _MainVSpeed);
    u_xlat11.xy = fract(u_xlat11.xy);
    u_xlat0.xy = (bool(u_xlatb0)) ? vs_TEXCOORD1.xy : u_xlat11.xy;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb22 = !!(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV3Main));
#else
    u_xlatb22 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV3Main);
#endif
    u_xlat22.xy = (bool(u_xlatb22)) ? vs_TEXCOORD3.xy : vs_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat22.xy = u_xlat22.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy + u_xlat22.xy;
    u_xlat22.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat22.xy = min(max(u_xlat22.xy, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat22.xy = clamp(u_xlat22.xy, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat22.xy = (-u_xlat0.xy) + u_xlat22.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = vec2(_ClampUVMainX, _ClampUVMainY) * u_xlat22.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, u_xlat0.xy);
    u_xlatb1.xy = notEqual(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0), vec4(_RAlpha, _IF_ADD_MODE, _RAlpha, _RAlpha)).xy;
    u_xlat16_2 = (u_xlatb1.x) ? u_xlat16_0.x : u_xlat16_0.w;
    u_xlat16_3 = _ColorBlack * vec4(_EmissionBlack);
    u_xlat16_4 = _ColorLight * vec4(_EmissionLight);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb33 = !!(0.5<_UseThreeColor);
#else
    u_xlatb33 = 0.5<_UseThreeColor;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb33){
        u_xlat16_5 = _ColorMiddle * vec4(_EmissionMiddle);
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = min(max(u_xlat16_6.xyz, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = clamp(u_xlat16_6.xyz, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_6.w = u_xlat16_2 + u_xlat16_2;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_6.w = min(max(u_xlat16_6.w, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_6.w = clamp(u_xlat16_6.w, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_7 = _ColorMiddle * vec4(_EmissionMiddle) + (-u_xlat16_3);
        u_xlat16_6 = u_xlat16_6 * u_xlat16_7 + u_xlat16_3;
        u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + vec3(-0.5, -0.5, -0.5);
        u_xlat16_7.w = u_xlat16_2 + -0.5;
        u_xlat16_7 = u_xlat16_7 + u_xlat16_7;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_7 = min(max(u_xlat16_7, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_7 = clamp(u_xlat16_7, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_8 = _ColorLight * vec4(_EmissionLight) + (-u_xlat16_5);
        u_xlat16_5 = u_xlat16_7 * u_xlat16_8 + u_xlat16_5;
        u_xlat16_5 = (-u_xlat16_6) + u_xlat16_5;
        u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
        u_xlat16_7.w = u_xlat16_2 * u_xlat16_5.w;
        u_xlat16_5 = u_xlat16_6 + u_xlat16_7;
    } else {
        u_xlat16_6 = _ColorLight * vec4(_EmissionLight) + (-u_xlat16_3);
        u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
        u_xlat16_7.w = u_xlat16_2 * u_xlat16_6.w;
        u_xlat16_5 = _ColorBlack * vec4(_EmissionBlack) + u_xlat16_7;
    }
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb33 = !!(unity_WorldTransformParams.w<0.0);
#else
    u_xlatb33 = unity_WorldTransformParams.w<0.0;
#endif
    u_xlat16_10 = (uint((gl_FrontFacing ? 0xffffffffu : uint(0))) != uint(0)) ? u_xlat16_3 : u_xlat16_4;
    u_xlat16_4 = (uint((gl_FrontFacing ? 0xffffffffu : uint(0))) != uint(0)) ? u_xlat16_4 : u_xlat16_3;
    u_xlat16_3 = u_xlat16_10;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.w = u_xlat16_2 * u_xlat16_4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.w = u_xlat16_2 * u_xlat16_3.w;
    u_xlat16_0 = (bool(u_xlatb33)) ? u_xlat16_6 : u_xlat16_4;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb1.x = !!(_CullMode<0.5);
#else
    u_xlatb1.x = _CullMode<0.5;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb23.x = !!(0.5<_TwoFace);
#else
    u_xlatb23.x = 0.5<_TwoFace;
#endif
    u_xlatb1.x = u_xlatb1.x && u_xlatb23.x;
    u_xlati1 = u_xlatb1.x ? 1 : int(0);
    u_xlat16_0 = (int(u_xlati1) != 0) ? u_xlat16_0 : u_xlat16_5;
    u_xlat1.x = _Time.y * _ColorFrequency;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.00318471342;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb23.x = !!(u_xlat1.x>=(-u_xlat1.x));
#else
    u_xlatb23.x = u_xlat1.x>=(-u_xlat1.x);
#endif
    u_xlat1.x = fract(abs(u_xlat1.x));
    u_xlat1.x = (u_xlatb23.x) ? u_xlat1.x : (-u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 314.0;
    u_xlat1.x = sin(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlatb23.xy = notEqual(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0), vec4(_IsLerpColor, _NoVertexColor, _IsLerpColor, _NoVertexColor)).xy;
    u_xlat3 = (-u_xlat16_0) + _ColorLerp;
    u_xlat3 = abs(u_xlat1.xxxx) * u_xlat3 + u_xlat16_0;
    u_xlat0 = (u_xlatb23.x) ? u_xlat3 : u_xlat16_0;
    u_xlat16_3 = (u_xlatb23.y) ? vec4(1.0, 1.0, 1.0, 1.0) : vs_COLOR0;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(vs_NORMAL0.xyz, vs_NORMAL0.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat1.xxx * vs_NORMAL0.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat42 = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat42 = inversesqrt(u_xlat42);
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat42) * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat1.xzw, u_xlat9.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.x = min(max(u_xlat1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat1.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_13.x = max(_FresnelPower, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.x = log2(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat1.x = exp2(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * _FresnelColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * vec3(vec3(_FresnelEmission, _FresnelEmission, _FresnelEmission));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat0.w * u_xlat16_2;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat1.x * _FresnelEmission;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_15 = _FresnelColor.w * _InvertFresnel + (-u_xlat16_2);
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_15 + u_xlat16_2;
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat0.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlatb9.xy = notEqual(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0), vec4(_UseUV2Mask, _UseUV3Mask, _UseUV2Mask, _UseUV2Mask)).xy;
    u_xlat31.xy = _Time.yy * vec2(_MaskUSpeed, _MaskVSpeed);
    u_xlat31.xy = fract(u_xlat31.xy);
    u_xlat9.xz = (u_xlatb9.x) ? vs_TEXCOORD2.xy : u_xlat31.xy;
    u_xlat20.xz = (u_xlatb9.y) ? vs_TEXCOORD3.xy : vs_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat20.xz = u_xlat20.xz * _MaskTex_ST.xy + _MaskTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xz + u_xlat20.xz;
    u_xlat31.xy = u_xlat9.xy;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat31.xy = min(max(u_xlat31.xy, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat31.xy = clamp(u_xlat31.xy, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat31.xy = (-u_xlat9.xy) + u_xlat31.xy;
    u_xlat9.xy = vec2(_ClampUVMaskX, _ClampUVMaskY) * u_xlat31.xy + u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat16_9 = texture(_MaskTex, u_xlat9.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_9 + (-_MaskIntensity);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_13.x = min(max(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_13.x = clamp(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_24 = (-_MaskIntensity) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_24 = _MaskFeatheredIntensity * u_xlat16_24 + 9.99999975e-05;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x / u_xlat16_24;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_13.x = min(max(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_13.x = clamp(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_2;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_2 * _Alpha;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_3.w * u_xlat16_2;
    u_xlat16_24 = (u_xlatb1.y) ? u_xlat16_13.x : 1.0;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xzw * vec3(u_xlat16_24);
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_2 * u_xlat16_3.w + (-_ClipValue);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb34 = !!(u_xlat16_2<0.0);
#else
    u_xlatb34 = u_xlat16_2<0.0;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb34){discard;}
    u_xlat16_2 = _SrcBlendFactor * _DstBlendFactor;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb34 = !!(u_xlat16_2==1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb34 = u_xlat16_2==1.0;
#endif
    SV_Target0.w = (u_xlatb34) ? 0.00100000005 : u_xlat16_13.x;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz;
    return;
}

#endif

SubProgram "gles " {
Local Keywords { "_DISSOLVE_ON" "_FRESNEL_ON" }
"// hash: 2bb8400305861722
#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
uniform 	mediump float _Zoffset;
uniform 	mediump float _RotateUV;
uniform 	mediump float _RotateUVAngle;
uniform 	mediump float _CylinderUV;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _CenterOffset;
uniform 	mediump float _Axis;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TEXCOORD1;
attribute highp vec4 in_TEXCOORD2;
attribute mediump vec4 in_COLOR0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TEXCOORD3;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD2;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_COLOR0;
varying highp vec3 vs_NORMAL0;
varying highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD4;
vec3 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
bool u_xlatb2;
vec2 u_xlat3;
vec2 u_xlat4;
vec2 u_xlat7;
bool u_xlatb7;
float u_xlat12;
bool u_xlatb12;
bool u_xlatb13;
float u_xlat15;
bool u_xlatb15;
float u_xlat17;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    u_xlatb15 = 0.5<_RotateUV;
    if(u_xlatb15){
        u_xlat15 = _RotateUVAngle * 0.0174532924;
        u_xlat2.x = sin(u_xlat15);
        u_xlat3.x = cos(u_xlat15);
        u_xlat7.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.yx + vec2(-0.5, -0.5);
        u_xlat2.xw = u_xlat7.xy * u_xlat2.xx;
        u_xlat15 = u_xlat3.x * u_xlat7.y + (-u_xlat2.x);
        u_xlat4.x = u_xlat15 + 0.5;
        u_xlat15 = u_xlat3.x * u_xlat7.x + u_xlat2.w;
        u_xlat4.y = u_xlat15 + 0.5;
    } else {
        u_xlat4.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    }
    u_xlat2.xyz = in_POSITION0.yzx + _CenterOffset.yzx;
    u_xlatb15 = _Axis<1.0;
    if(u_xlatb15){
        u_xlat3.y = u_xlat2.z;
    } else {
        u_xlatb15 = _Axis==1.0;
        u_xlat3.xy = (bool(u_xlatb15)) ? u_xlat2.yx : u_xlat2.xy;
        u_xlat2.w = u_xlat3.x;
        u_xlat2.xy = u_xlat2.zw;
    }
    u_xlat15 = min(abs(u_xlat2.x), abs(u_xlat2.y));
    u_xlat12 = max(abs(u_xlat2.x), abs(u_xlat2.y));
    u_xlat12 = float(1.0) / u_xlat12;
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat15 * u_xlat12;
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat15 * u_xlat15;
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat12 * 0.0208350997 + -0.0851330012;
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat12 * u_xlat17 + 0.180141002;
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat12 * u_xlat17 + -0.330299497;
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat12 * u_xlat17 + 0.999866009;
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat15 * u_xlat12;
    u_xlatb13 = abs(u_xlat2.x)<abs(u_xlat2.y);
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat17 * -2.0 + 1.57079637;
    u_xlat17 = u_xlatb13 ? u_xlat17 : float(0.0);
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat15 * u_xlat12 + u_xlat17;
    u_xlatb12 = u_xlat2.x<(-u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat12 = u_xlatb12 ? -3.14159274 : float(0.0);
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat15 + u_xlat12;
    u_xlat12 = min(u_xlat2.x, u_xlat2.y);
    u_xlat2.x = max(u_xlat2.x, u_xlat2.y);
    u_xlatb7 = u_xlat12<(-u_xlat12);
    u_xlatb2 = u_xlat2.x>=(-u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlatb2 = u_xlatb2 && u_xlatb7;
    u_xlat15 = (u_xlatb2) ? (-u_xlat15) : u_xlat15;
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat15 * 0.159154937 + 0.5;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat15 + _CenterOffset.w;
    u_xlatb15 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_CylinderUV);
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = (bool(u_xlatb15)) ? u_xlat3.xy : u_xlat4.xy;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    vs_NORMAL0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = _Zoffset / u_xlat1.w;
    gl_Position.z = (-u_xlat15) + u_xlat1.z;
    gl_Position.xyw = u_xlat1.xyw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = vec2(0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = in_TEXCOORD1;
    vs_TEXCOORD2 = in_TEXCOORD2;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = in_TEXCOORD3;
    vs_COLOR0 = in_COLOR0;
    vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    return;
}

#ifdef FRAGMENT

#ifdef GL_FRAGMENT_PRECISION_HIGH
    precision highp float;

precision highp int;

uniform 	vec4 _EdgeColor;

varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;

varying mediump vec4 vs_COLOR0;
varying highp vec3 vs_NORMAL0;
varying highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD4;
#define SV_Target0 gl_FragData[0]
vec4 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
lowp vec4 u_xlat10_0;
bool u_xlatb0;

int u_xlati1;
bvec2 u_xlatb1;
mediump float u_xlat16_2;

mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;

bool u_xlatb9;

vec2 u_xlat12;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_14;
mediump float u_xlat16_16;
vec2 u_xlat21;
bool u_xlatb21;
float u_xlat22;
vec2 u_xlat24;
bool u_xlatb24;
bvec2 u_xlatb25;
vec2 u_xlat33;
bool u_xlatb36;
bool u_xlatb37;
float u_xlat45;
void main()
{
    u_xlatb0 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV1);
    u_xlat12.xy = _Time.yy * vec2(_MainUSpeed, _MainVSpeed);
    u_xlat12.xy = fract(u_xlat12.xy);
    u_xlat0.xy = (bool(u_xlatb0)) ? vs_TEXCOORD1.xy : u_xlat12.xy;
    u_xlatb24 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV3Main);
    u_xlat24.xy = (bool(u_xlatb24)) ? vs_TEXCOORD3.xy : vs_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat24.xy = u_xlat24.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy + u_xlat24.xy;
    u_xlat24.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat24.xy = clamp(u_xlat24.xy, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat24.xy = (-u_xlat0.xy) + u_xlat24.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = vec2(_ClampUVMainX, _ClampUVMainY) * u_xlat24.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat10_0 = texture2D(_MainTex, u_xlat0.xy);
    u_xlatb1.xy = notEqual(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0), vec4(_RAlpha, _IF_ADD_MODE, _RAlpha, _RAlpha)).xy;
    u_xlat16_2 = (u_xlatb1.x) ? u_xlat10_0.x : u_xlat10_0.w;
    u_xlat16_3 = _ColorBlack * vec4(_EmissionBlack);
    u_xlat16_4 = _ColorLight * vec4(_EmissionLight);
    u_xlatb36 = 0.5<_UseThreeColor;
    if(u_xlatb36){
        u_xlat16_5 = _ColorMiddle * vec4(_EmissionMiddle);
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz + u_xlat10_0.xyz;
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = clamp(u_xlat16_6.xyz, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_6.w = u_xlat16_2 + u_xlat16_2;
        u_xlat16_6.w = clamp(u_xlat16_6.w, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_7 = _ColorMiddle * vec4(_EmissionMiddle) + (-u_xlat16_3);
        u_xlat16_6 = u_xlat16_6 * u_xlat16_7 + u_xlat16_3;
        u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz + vec3(-0.5, -0.5, -0.5);
        u_xlat16_7.w = u_xlat16_2 + -0.5;
        u_xlat16_7 = u_xlat16_7 + u_xlat16_7;
        u_xlat16_7 = clamp(u_xlat16_7, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_8 = _ColorLight * vec4(_EmissionLight) + (-u_xlat16_5);
        u_xlat16_5 = u_xlat16_7 * u_xlat16_8 + u_xlat16_5;
        u_xlat16_5 = (-u_xlat16_6) + u_xlat16_5;
        u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
        u_xlat16_7.w = u_xlat16_2 * u_xlat16_5.w;
        u_xlat16_5 = u_xlat16_6 + u_xlat16_7;
    } else {
        u_xlat16_6 = _ColorLight * vec4(_EmissionLight) + (-u_xlat16_3);
        u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
        u_xlat16_7.w = u_xlat16_2 * u_xlat16_6.w;
        u_xlat16_5 = _ColorBlack * vec4(_EmissionBlack) + u_xlat16_7;

    u_xlat16_11 = (int((gl_FrontFacing ? 1 : 0)) != 0) ? u_xlat16_3 : u_xlat16_4;
    u_xlat16_4 = (int((gl_FrontFacing ? 1 : 0)) != 0) ? u_xlat16_4 : u_xlat16_3;
    u_xlat16_3 = u_xlat16_11;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.w = u_xlat16_2 * u_xlat16_4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.w = u_xlat16_2 * u_xlat16_3.w;
    u_xlat16_0 = (bool(u_xlatb36)) ? u_xlat16_6 : u_xlat16_4;
    u_xlatb1.x = _CullMode<0.5;
    u_xlatb25.x = 0.5<_TwoFace;
    u_xlatb1.x = u_xlatb1.x && u_xlatb25.x;
    u_xlati1 = u_xlatb1.x ? 1 : int(0);
    u_xlat16_0 = (int(u_xlati1) != 0) ? u_xlat16_0 : u_xlat16_5;
    u_xlat1.x = _Time.y * _ColorFrequency;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.00318471342;
    u_xlatb25.x = u_xlat1.x>=(-u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.x = fract(abs(u_xlat1.x));
    u_xlat1.x = (u_xlatb25.x) ? u_xlat1.x : (-u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 314.0;
    u_xlat1.x = sin(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlatb25.xy = notEqual(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0), vec4(_IsLerpColor, _NoVertexColor, _IsLerpColor, _NoVertexColor)).xy;

    u_xlat3 = abs(u_xlat1.xxxx) * u_xlat3 + u_xlat16_0;
    u_xlat0 = (u_xlatb25.x) ? u_xlat3 : u_xlat16_0;
    u_xlat16_3 = (u_xlatb25.y) ? vec4(1.0, 1.0, 1.0, 1.0) : vs_COLOR0;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(vs_NORMAL0.xyz, vs_NORMAL0.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat1.xxx * vs_NORMAL0.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat45 = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat45 = inversesqrt(u_xlat45);
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat45) * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat1.xzw, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat1.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_14.x = max(_FresnelPower, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.x = log2(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat16_14.x;
    u_xlat1.x = exp2(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * _FresnelColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xyz * vec3(vec3(_FresnelEmission, _FresnelEmission, _FresnelEmission));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat0.w * u_xlat16_2;

    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);

    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat0.xyz + u_xlat16_14.xyz;
    u_xlatb9 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV2DissolveOffset);

    u_xlat9.xy = (bool(u_xlatb9)) ? vs_TEXCOORD2.zw : u_xlat21.xy;

    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xy + u_xlat33.xy;
    u_xlat33.xy = u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat33.xy = clamp(u_xlat33.xy, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat33.xy = (-u_xlat9.xy) + u_xlat33.xy;

    u_xlat10_9 = texture2D(_DissolveTex, u_xlat9.xy).x;
    u_xlatb21 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV1Dissolve);
    u_xlat21.x = (u_xlatb21) ? vs_TEXCOORD1.z : _DissolveRange;
    u_xlat33.x = (-_DissolveEdge) + 1.0;
    u_xlat45 = (-u_xlat21.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat45 = (-u_xlat45) + u_xlat21.x;
    u_xlat45 = u_xlat45 + u_xlat10_9;
    u_xlat10.x = (-u_xlat33.x) + _DissolveEdge;
    u_xlat45 = (-u_xlat33.x) + u_xlat45;
    u_xlat10.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat10.x;
    u_xlat45 = u_xlat45 * u_xlat10.x;
    u_xlat45 = clamp(u_xlat45, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat22 = u_xlat45 * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat45 = u_xlat45 * u_xlat45;
    u_xlat45 = u_xlat45 * u_xlat22;
    u_xlat16_14.x = _ColorEdgeWidth * 1.39999998 + -0.400000006;
    u_xlat21.x = (-u_xlat16_14.x) + u_xlat21.x;
    u_xlat22 = (-u_xlat21.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat21.x = u_xlat21.x + (-u_xlat22);
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat10_9 + u_xlat21.x;
    u_xlat9.x = (-u_xlat33.x) + u_xlat9.x;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat10.x * u_xlat9.x;
    u_xlat9.x = clamp(u_xlat9.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat21.x = u_xlat9.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat9.x * u_xlat9.x;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat9.x * u_xlat21.x;
    u_xlat10.xyz = _EdgeColor.xyz * vec3(_EdgeEmission);
    u_xlat21.x = u_xlat16_2 * u_xlat45;
    u_xlat1.xzw = (-_EdgeColor.xyz) * vec3(_EdgeEmission) + u_xlat1.xzw;
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat9.xxx * u_xlat1.xzw + u_xlat10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat21.x * _Alpha;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_3.w * u_xlat16_2;
    u_xlat16_14.x = (u_xlatb1.y) ? u_xlat16_2 : 1.0;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xzw * u_xlat16_14.xxx;
    u_xlat16_14.x = _SrcBlendFactor * _DstBlendFactor;
    u_xlatb37 = u_xlat16_14.x==1.0;
    SV_Target0.w = (u_xlatb37) ? 0.00100000005 : u_xlat16_2;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz;
    return;
}

out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;

vec3 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
bool u_xlatb2;
vec2 u_xlat3;
vec2 u_xlat4;
vec2 u_xlat7;
bool u_xlatb7;
float u_xlat12;
bool u_xlatb12;
bool u_xlatb13;
float u_xlat15;
bool u_xlatb15;
float u_xlat17;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb15 = !!(0.5<_RotateUV);
#else
    u_xlatb15 = 0.5<_RotateUV;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb15){
        u_xlat15 = _RotateUVAngle * 0.0174532924;
        u_xlat2.x = sin(u_xlat15);
        u_xlat3.x = cos(u_xlat15);
        u_xlat7.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.yx + vec2(-0.5, -0.5);
        u_xlat2.xw = u_xlat7.xy * u_xlat2.xx;
        u_xlat15 = u_xlat3.x * u_xlat7.y + (-u_xlat2.x);
        u_xlat4.x = u_xlat15 + 0.5;
        u_xlat15 = u_xlat3.x * u_xlat7.x + u_xlat2.w;
        u_xlat4.y = u_xlat15 + 0.5;
    } else {
        u_xlat4.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    }
    u_xlat2.xyz = in_POSITION0.yzx + _CenterOffset.yzx;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb15 = !!(_Axis<1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb15 = _Axis<1.0;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb15){
        u_xlat3.y = u_xlat2.z;
    } else {
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb15 = !!(_Axis==1.0);
#else
        u_xlatb15 = _Axis==1.0;
#endif
        u_xlat3.xy = (bool(u_xlatb15)) ? u_xlat2.yx : u_xlat2.xy;
        u_xlat2.w = u_xlat3.x;
        u_xlat2.xy = u_xlat2.zw;
    }
    u_xlat15 = min(abs(u_xlat2.x), abs(u_xlat2.y));
    u_xlat12 = max(abs(u_xlat2.x), abs(u_xlat2.y));
    u_xlat12 = float(1.0) / u_xlat12;
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat15 * u_xlat12;
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat15 * u_xlat15;
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat12 * 0.0208350997 + -0.0851330012;
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat12 * u_xlat17 + 0.180141002;
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat12 * u_xlat17 + -0.330299497;
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat12 * u_xlat17 + 0.999866009;
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat15 * u_xlat12;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb13 = !!(abs(u_xlat2.x)<abs(u_xlat2.y));
#else
    u_xlatb13 = abs(u_xlat2.x)<abs(u_xlat2.y);
#endif
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat17 * -2.0 + 1.57079637;
    u_xlat17 = u_xlatb13 ? u_xlat17 : float(0.0);
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat15 * u_xlat12 + u_xlat17;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb12 = !!(u_xlat2.x<(-u_xlat2.x));
#else
    u_xlatb12 = u_xlat2.x<(-u_xlat2.x);
#endif
    u_xlat12 = u_xlatb12 ? -3.14159274 : float(0.0);
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat15 + u_xlat12;
    u_xlat12 = min(u_xlat2.x, u_xlat2.y);
    u_xlat2.x = max(u_xlat2.x, u_xlat2.y);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb7 = !!(u_xlat12<(-u_xlat12));
#else
    u_xlatb7 = u_xlat12<(-u_xlat12);
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb2 = !!(u_xlat2.x>=(-u_xlat2.x));
#else
    u_xlatb2 = u_xlat2.x>=(-u_xlat2.x);
#endif
    u_xlatb2 = u_xlatb2 && u_xlatb7;
    u_xlat15 = (u_xlatb2) ? (-u_xlat15) : u_xlat15;
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat15 * 0.159154937 + 0.5;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat15 + _CenterOffset.w;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb15 = !!(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_CylinderUV));
#else
    u_xlatb15 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_CylinderUV);
#endif
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = (bool(u_xlatb15)) ? u_xlat3.xy : u_xlat4.xy;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    vs_NORMAL0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = _Zoffset / u_xlat1.w;
    gl_Position.z = (-u_xlat15) + u_xlat1.z;
    gl_Position.xyw = u_xlat1.xyw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = vec2(0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = in_TEXCOORD1;
    vs_TEXCOORD2 = in_TEXCOORD2;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = in_TEXCOORD3;
    vs_COLOR0 = in_COLOR0;
    vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    return;
}

#endif

uniform 	vec4 _Time;
