precision highp int;
uniform 	vec4 _Time;
uniform 	mediump vec4 unity_WorldTransformParams;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _ColorLight;
uniform 	mediump float _EmissionLight;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _ColorBlack;
uniform 	mediump float _EmissionBlack;
uniform 	mediump float _UseThreeColor;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _ColorMiddle;
uniform 	mediump float _EmissionMiddle;
uniform 	mediump float _Alpha;
uniform 	mediump float _UseUV1;
uniform 	mediump float _MainUSpeed;
uniform 	mediump float _MainVSpeed;
uniform 	mediump float _NoVertexColor;
uniform 	mediump float _IsLerpColor;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _ColorLerp;
uniform 	mediump float _ColorFrequency;
uniform 	mediump float _ClampUVMainX;
uniform 	mediump float _ClampUVMainY;
uniform 	mediump float _RAlpha;
uniform 	mediump float _IF_ADD_MODE;
uniform 	mediump float _SrcBlendFactor;
uniform 	mediump float _DstBlendFactor;
uniform 	mediump float _CullMode;
uniform 	mediump float _TwoFace;
uniform 	mediump float _UseUV3Main;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MaskTex_ST;
uniform 	mediump float _MaskUSpeed;
uniform 	mediump float _MaskVSpeed;
uniform 	mediump float _MaskIntensity;
uniform 	mediump float _MaskFeatheredIntensity;
uniform 	mediump float _ClampUVMaskX;
uniform 	mediump float _ClampUVMaskY;
uniform 	mediump float _UseUV2Mask;
uniform 	mediump float _UseUV3Mask;
uniform 	vec4 _DissolveTex_ST;
uniform 	float _DissolveUSpeed;
uniform 	float _DissolveVSpeed;
uniform 	float _DissolveEdge;
uniform 	float _DissolveRange;
uniform 	float _UseUV1Dissolve;
uniform 	float _ClampUVDissolve;
uniform 	float _ColorEdgeWidth;
uniform 	vec4 _EdgeColor;
uniform 	float _EdgeEmission;
uniform 	float _UseUV2DissolveOffset;
uniform lowp sampler2D _MainTex;
uniform lowp sampler2D _MaskTex;
uniform lowp sampler2D _DissolveTex;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD2;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_COLOR0;
#define SV_Target0 gl_FragData[0]
vec4 u_xlat0;
lowp vec4 u_xlat10_0;
int u_xlati0;
bool u_xlatb0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
bvec3 u_xlatb1;
mediump float u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
vec2 u_xlat10;
bvec2 u_xlatb10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
float u_xlat18;
vec2 u_xlat20;
lowp float u_xlat10_20;
bool u_xlatb20;
float u_xlat21;
mediump float u_xlat16_22;
bool u_xlatb30;
float u_xlat31;
void main()
{
    u_xlatb0 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV1);
    u_xlat10.xy = _Time.yy * vec2(_MainUSpeed, _MainVSpeed);
    u_xlat10.xy = fract(u_xlat10.xy);
    u_xlat0.xy = (bool(u_xlatb0)) ? vs_TEXCOORD1.xy : u_xlat10.xy;
    u_xlatb20 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV3Main);
    u_xlat20.xy = (bool(u_xlatb20)) ? vs_TEXCOORD3.xy : vs_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat20.xy = u_xlat20.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy + u_xlat20.xy;
    u_xlat20.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat20.xy = clamp(u_xlat20.xy, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat20.xy = (-u_xlat0.xy) + u_xlat20.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = vec2(_ClampUVMainX, _ClampUVMainY) * u_xlat20.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat10_0 = texture2D(_MainTex, u_xlat0.xy);
    u_xlatb1.xy = notEqual(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0), vec4(_RAlpha, _IF_ADD_MODE, _RAlpha, _RAlpha)).xy;
    u_xlat16_2 = (u_xlatb1.x) ? u_xlat10_0.x : u_xlat10_0.w;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = _ColorBlack.xyz * vec3(_EmissionBlack);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = _ColorLight.xyz * vec3(_EmissionLight);
    u_xlatb30 = 0.5<_UseThreeColor;
    if(u_xlatb30){
        u_xlat16_4.xyz = _ColorMiddle.xyz * vec3(_EmissionMiddle);
        u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz + u_xlat10_0.xyz;
        u_xlat16_5.xyz = clamp(u_xlat16_5.xyz, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = _ColorMiddle.xyz * vec3(_EmissionMiddle) + (-u_xlat16_12.xyz);
        u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz + vec3(-0.5, -0.5, -0.5);
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = clamp(u_xlat16_6.xyz, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_7.xyz = _ColorLight.xyz * vec3(_EmissionLight) + (-u_xlat16_4.xyz);
        u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
        u_xlat16_4.xyz = (-u_xlat16_5.xyz) + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
        u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    } else {
        u_xlat16_5.xyz = _ColorLight.xyz * vec3(_EmissionLight) + (-u_xlat16_12.xyz);
        u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    }
    u_xlatb30 = unity_WorldTransformParams.w<0.0;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = (int((gl_FrontFacing ? 1 : 0)) != 0) ? u_xlat16_12.xyz : u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = (int((gl_FrontFacing ? 1 : 0)) != 0) ? u_xlat16_3.xyz : u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = (bool(u_xlatb30)) ? u_xlat16_12.xyz : u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlatb0 = _CullMode<0.5;
    u_xlatb10.x = 0.5<_TwoFace;
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlatb0 && u_xlatb10.x;
    u_xlati0 = u_xlatb0 ? 1 : int(0);
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = (int(u_xlati0) != 0) ? u_xlat16_12.xyz : u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = _Time.y * _ColorFrequency;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 0.00318471342;
    u_xlatb10.x = u_xlat0.x>=(-u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat0.x = fract(abs(u_xlat0.x));
    u_xlat0.x = (u_xlatb10.x) ? u_xlat0.x : (-u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 314.0;
    u_xlat0.x = sin(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlatb10.xy = notEqual(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0), vec4(_IsLerpColor, _NoVertexColor, _IsLerpColor, _IsLerpColor)).xy;
    u_xlat1.xzw = (-u_xlat16_12.xyz) + _ColorLerp.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xzw = abs(u_xlat0.xxx) * u_xlat1.xzw + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (u_xlatb10.x) ? u_xlat1.xzw : u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3 = (u_xlatb10.y) ? vec4(1.0, 1.0, 1.0, 1.0) : vs_COLOR0;
    u_xlatb1.xz = notEqual(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0), vec4(_UseUV2Mask, _UseUV2Mask, _UseUV3Mask, _UseUV2Mask)).xz;
    u_xlat8.xy = _Time.yy * vec2(_MaskUSpeed, _MaskVSpeed);
    u_xlat8.xy = fract(u_xlat8.xy);
    u_xlat1.xw = (u_xlatb1.x) ? vs_TEXCOORD2.xy : u_xlat8.xy;
    u_xlat8.xy = (u_xlatb1.z) ? vs_TEXCOORD3.xy : vs_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat8.xy = u_xlat8.xy * _MaskTex_ST.xy + _MaskTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat1.xz = u_xlat1.xw + u_xlat8.xy;
    u_xlat8.xy = u_xlat1.xz;
    u_xlat8.xy = clamp(u_xlat8.xy, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat8.xy = (-u_xlat1.xz) + u_xlat8.xy;
    u_xlat1.xz = vec2(_ClampUVMaskX, _ClampUVMaskY) * u_xlat8.xy + u_xlat1.xz;
    u_xlat10_20 = texture2D(_MaskTex, u_xlat1.xz).x;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat10_20 + (-_MaskIntensity);
    u_xlat16_12.x = clamp(u_xlat16_12.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_22 = (-_MaskIntensity) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_22 = _MaskFeatheredIntensity * u_xlat16_22 + 9.99999975e-05;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_12.x / u_xlat16_22;
    u_xlat16_12.x = clamp(u_xlat16_12.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_2;
    u_xlatb20 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV2DissolveOffset);
    u_xlat1.xz = _Time.yy * vec2(_DissolveUSpeed, _DissolveVSpeed);
    u_xlat1.xz = fract(u_xlat1.xz);
    u_xlat1.xz = (bool(u_xlatb20)) ? vs_TEXCOORD2.zw : u_xlat1.xz;
    u_xlat8.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DissolveTex_ST.xy + _DissolveTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat1.xz = u_xlat1.xz + u_xlat8.xy;
    u_xlat8.xy = u_xlat1.xz;
    u_xlat8.xy = clamp(u_xlat8.xy, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat8.xy = (-u_xlat1.xz) + u_xlat8.xy;
    u_xlat1.xz = vec2(vec2(_ClampUVDissolve, _ClampUVDissolve)) * u_xlat8.xy + u_xlat1.xz;
    u_xlat10_20 = texture2D(_DissolveTex, u_xlat1.xz).x;
    u_xlatb1.x = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV1Dissolve);
    u_xlat1.x = (u_xlatb1.x) ? vs_TEXCOORD1.z : _DissolveRange;
    u_xlat21 = (-_DissolveEdge) + 1.0;
    u_xlat31 = (-u_xlat1.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat31 = (-u_xlat31) + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat31 = u_xlat10_20 + u_xlat31;
    u_xlat8.x = (-u_xlat21) + _DissolveEdge;
    u_xlat31 = (-u_xlat21) + u_xlat31;
    u_xlat8.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat8.x;
    u_xlat31 = u_xlat31 * u_xlat8.x;
    u_xlat31 = clamp(u_xlat31, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat31 * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat31 = u_xlat31 * u_xlat31;
    u_xlat31 = u_xlat31 * u_xlat18;
    u_xlat16_12.x = _ColorEdgeWidth * 1.39999998 + -0.400000006;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x + (-u_xlat16_12.x);
    u_xlat18 = (-u_xlat1.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x + (-u_xlat18);
    u_xlat20.x = u_xlat10_20 + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat20.x = (-u_xlat21) + u_xlat20.x;
    u_xlat20.x = u_xlat8.x * u_xlat20.x;
    u_xlat20.x = clamp(u_xlat20.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat20.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat20.x = u_xlat20.x * u_xlat20.x;
    u_xlat20.x = u_xlat20.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat8.xyz = _EdgeColor.xyz * vec3(_EdgeEmission);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat31 * u_xlat16_2;
    u_xlat0.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat0.xyw + (-u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat20.xxx * u_xlat0.xyw + u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat1.x * _Alpha;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_3.w * u_xlat16_2;
    u_xlat16_12.x = (u_xlatb1.y) ? u_xlat16_2 : 1.0;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_12.xxx;
    u_xlat16_12.x = _SrcBlendFactor * _DstBlendFactor;
    u_xlatb30 = u_xlat16_12.x==1.0;
    SV_Target0.w = (u_xlatb30) ? 0.00100000005 : u_xlat16_2;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}

UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _DisturbTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
in highp vec4 in_TEXCOORD1;
in highp vec4 in_TEXCOORD2;
in mediump vec4 in_COLOR0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TEXCOORD3;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_COLOR0;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
mediump float u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
bool u_xlatb3;
float u_xlat4;
bool u_xlatb4;
vec2 u_xlat5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
mediump float u_xlat16_6;
bool u_xlatb6;
mediump float u_xlat16_7;
vec2 u_xlat9;
bool u_xlatb10;
vec2 u_xlat12;
float u_xlat15;
bool u_xlatb15;
float u_xlat21;
bool u_xlatb21;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DisturbTex_ST.xy + _DisturbTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat12.xy = _Time.yy * vec2(_DisturbUSpeed, _DisturbVSpeed);
    u_xlat12.xy = fract(u_xlat12.xy);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat12.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_DisturbTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x + -0.5;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb6 = !!(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_DisturbAnimToggle));
#else
    u_xlatb6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_DisturbAnimToggle);
#endif
    u_xlat6.xyz = (bool(u_xlatb6)) ? _DisturbVector.xyz : in_NORMAL0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6 = u_xlat6.x + 0.00100000005;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat0.x * _VertAmplitude;
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat16_6;
    u_xlat16_7 = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_7);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_7);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_1) * u_xlat16_2.xyz + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3];
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3] * u_xlat0.wwww + u_xlat1;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb3 = !!(0.5<_RotateUV);
#else
    u_xlatb3 = 0.5<_RotateUV;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb3){
        u_xlat3.x = _RotateUVAngle * 0.0174532924;
        u_xlat4 = cos(u_xlat3.x);
        u_xlat3.x = sin(u_xlat3.x);
        u_xlat9.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.yx + vec2(-0.5, -0.5);
        u_xlat3.xw = u_xlat9.xy * u_xlat3.xx;
        u_xlat3.x = u_xlat4 * u_xlat9.y + (-u_xlat3.x);
        u_xlat5.x = u_xlat3.x + 0.5;
        u_xlat3.x = u_xlat4 * u_xlat9.x + u_xlat3.w;
        u_xlat5.y = u_xlat3.x + 0.5;
    } else {
        u_xlat5.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    }
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.yzx + _CenterOffset.yzx;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb3 = !!(_Axis<1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb3 = _Axis<1.0;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb3){
        u_xlat3.y = u_xlat1.z;
    } else {
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb15 = !!(_Axis==1.0);
#else
        u_xlatb15 = _Axis==1.0;
#endif
        u_xlat3.xy = (bool(u_xlatb15)) ? u_xlat1.yx : u_xlat1.xy;
        u_xlat1.w = u_xlat3.x;
        u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat1.zw;
    }
    u_xlat15 = min(abs(u_xlat1.x), abs(u_xlat1.y));
    u_xlat21 = max(abs(u_xlat1.x), abs(u_xlat1.y));
    u_xlat21 = float(1.0) / u_xlat21;
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat21 * u_xlat15;
    u_xlat21 = u_xlat15 * u_xlat15;
    u_xlat4 = u_xlat21 * 0.0208350997 + -0.0851330012;
    u_xlat4 = u_xlat21 * u_xlat4 + 0.180141002;
    u_xlat4 = u_xlat21 * u_xlat4 + -0.330299497;
    u_xlat21 = u_xlat21 * u_xlat4 + 0.999866009;
    u_xlat4 = u_xlat21 * u_xlat15;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb10 = !!(abs(u_xlat1.x)<abs(u_xlat1.y));
#else
    u_xlatb10 = abs(u_xlat1.x)<abs(u_xlat1.y);
#endif
    u_xlat4 = u_xlat4 * -2.0 + 1.57079637;
    u_xlat4 = u_xlatb10 ? u_xlat4 : float(0.0);
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat15 * u_xlat21 + u_xlat4;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb21 = !!(u_xlat1.x<(-u_xlat1.x));
#else
    u_xlatb21 = u_xlat1.x<(-u_xlat1.x);
#endif
    u_xlat21 = u_xlatb21 ? -3.14159274 : float(0.0);
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat21 + u_xlat15;
    u_xlat21 = min(u_xlat1.x, u_xlat1.y);
    u_xlat4 = max(u_xlat1.x, u_xlat1.y);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb21 = !!(u_xlat21<(-u_xlat21));
#else
    u_xlatb21 = u_xlat21<(-u_xlat21);
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb4 = !!(u_xlat4>=(-u_xlat4));
#else
    u_xlatb4 = u_xlat4>=(-u_xlat4);
#endif
    u_xlatb21 = u_xlatb21 && u_xlatb4;
    u_xlat15 = (u_xlatb21) ? (-u_xlat15) : u_xlat15;
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat15 * 0.159154937 + 0.5;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat15 + _CenterOffset.w;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb15 = !!(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_CylinderUV));
#else
    u_xlatb15 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_CylinderUV);
#endif
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = (bool(u_xlatb15)) ? u_xlat3.xy : u_xlat5.xy;
    u_xlat3.x = _Zoffset / u_xlat0.w;
    gl_Position.z = u_xlat0.z + (-u_xlat3.x);
    gl_Position.xyw = u_xlat0.xyw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = vec2(0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = in_TEXCOORD1;
    vs_TEXCOORD2 = in_TEXCOORD2;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = in_TEXCOORD3;
    vs_COLOR0 = in_COLOR0;
    return;
}

#endif

#endif
uniform 	vec4 _Time;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(0) uniform UnityPerDraw {

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _EmissionLight;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _ColorBlack;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _EmissionBlack;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _UseThreeColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _ColorMiddle;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _EmissionMiddle;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Alpha;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RowNum;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ClampUVMainX;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ClampUVMainY;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RotateUV;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RotateUVAngle;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RAlpha;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _IF_ADD_MODE;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SrcBlendFactor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DstBlendFactor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _CylinderUV;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _CenterOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Axis;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _CullMode;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _TwoFace;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _UseUV3Main;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _FlipAnim;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _flipCycle;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _flipOffset;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _UseUV1Noise;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MaskTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MaskUSpeed;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MaskVSpeed;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MaskIntensity;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MaskFeatheredIntensity;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ClampUVMaskX;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ClampUVMaskY;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _UseUV2Mask;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _UseUV3Mask;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _DissolveTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _DissolveUSpeed;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _DissolveVSpeed;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _DissolveEdge;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _DissolveRange;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _UseUV1Dissolve;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _ClampUVDissolve;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _ColorEdgeWidth;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _EdgeColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _EdgeEmission;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _UseUV2DissolveOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _FresnelColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _FresnelPower;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _FresnelEmission;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _InvertFresnel;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _DisturbVector;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _DisturbTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DisturbUSpeed;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DisturbVSpeed;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DisturbAnimToggle;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _VertAmplitude;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MaskTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _DissolveTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD2;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_COLOR0;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec4 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
int u_xlati0;
bool u_xlatb0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
bvec3 u_xlatb1;
mediump float u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
vec2 u_xlat10;
bvec2 u_xlatb10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
float u_xlat18;
vec2 u_xlat20;
mediump float u_xlat16_20;
bool u_xlatb20;
float u_xlat21;
mediump float u_xlat16_22;
bool u_xlatb30;
float u_xlat31;
void main()
{
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV1));
#else
    u_xlatb0 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV1);
#endif
    u_xlat10.xy = _Time.yy * vec2(_MainUSpeed, _MainVSpeed);
    u_xlat10.xy = fract(u_xlat10.xy);
    u_xlat0.xy = (bool(u_xlatb0)) ? vs_TEXCOORD1.xy : u_xlat10.xy;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb20 = !!(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV3Main));
#else
    u_xlatb20 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV3Main);
#endif
    u_xlat20.xy = (bool(u_xlatb20)) ? vs_TEXCOORD3.xy : vs_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat20.xy = u_xlat20.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy + u_xlat20.xy;
    u_xlat20.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat20.xy = min(max(u_xlat20.xy, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat20.xy = clamp(u_xlat20.xy, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat20.xy = (-u_xlat0.xy) + u_xlat20.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = vec2(_ClampUVMainX, _ClampUVMainY) * u_xlat20.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, u_xlat0.xy);
    u_xlatb1.xy = notEqual(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0), vec4(_RAlpha, _IF_ADD_MODE, _RAlpha, _RAlpha)).xy;
    u_xlat16_2 = (u_xlatb1.x) ? u_xlat16_0.x : u_xlat16_0.w;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = _ColorBlack.xyz * vec3(_EmissionBlack);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = _ColorLight.xyz * vec3(_EmissionLight);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb30 = !!(0.5<_UseThreeColor);
#else
    u_xlatb30 = 0.5<_UseThreeColor;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb30){
        u_xlat16_4.xyz = _ColorMiddle.xyz * vec3(_EmissionMiddle);
        u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_5.xyz = min(max(u_xlat16_5.xyz, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_5.xyz = clamp(u_xlat16_5.xyz, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = _ColorMiddle.xyz * vec3(_EmissionMiddle) + (-u_xlat16_12.xyz);
        u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + vec3(-0.5, -0.5, -0.5);
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = min(max(u_xlat16_6.xyz, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = clamp(u_xlat16_6.xyz, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_7.xyz = _ColorLight.xyz * vec3(_EmissionLight) + (-u_xlat16_4.xyz);
        u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
        u_xlat16_4.xyz = (-u_xlat16_5.xyz) + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
        u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    } else {
        u_xlat16_5.xyz = _ColorLight.xyz * vec3(_EmissionLight) + (-u_xlat16_12.xyz);
        u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    }
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb30 = !!(unity_WorldTransformParams.w<0.0);
#else
    u_xlatb30 = unity_WorldTransformParams.w<0.0;
#endif
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = (uint((gl_FrontFacing ? 0xffffffffu : uint(0))) != uint(0)) ? u_xlat16_12.xyz : u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = (uint((gl_FrontFacing ? 0xffffffffu : uint(0))) != uint(0)) ? u_xlat16_3.xyz : u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = (bool(u_xlatb30)) ? u_xlat16_12.xyz : u_xlat16_3.xyz;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(_CullMode<0.5);
#else
    u_xlatb0 = _CullMode<0.5;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb10.x = !!(0.5<_TwoFace);
#else
    u_xlatb10.x = 0.5<_TwoFace;
#endif
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlatb0 && u_xlatb10.x;
    u_xlati0 = u_xlatb0 ? 1 : int(0);
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = (int(u_xlati0) != 0) ? u_xlat16_12.xyz : u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = _Time.y * _ColorFrequency;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 0.00318471342;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb10.x = !!(u_xlat0.x>=(-u_xlat0.x));
#else
    u_xlatb10.x = u_xlat0.x>=(-u_xlat0.x);
#endif
    u_xlat0.x = fract(abs(u_xlat0.x));
    u_xlat0.x = (u_xlatb10.x) ? u_xlat0.x : (-u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 314.0;
    u_xlat0.x = sin(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlatb10.xy = notEqual(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0), vec4(_IsLerpColor, _NoVertexColor, _IsLerpColor, _IsLerpColor)).xy;
    u_xlat1.xzw = (-u_xlat16_12.xyz) + _ColorLerp.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xzw = abs(u_xlat0.xxx) * u_xlat1.xzw + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (u_xlatb10.x) ? u_xlat1.xzw : u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3 = (u_xlatb10.y) ? vec4(1.0, 1.0, 1.0, 1.0) : vs_COLOR0;
    u_xlatb1.xz = notEqual(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0), vec4(_UseUV2Mask, _UseUV2Mask, _UseUV3Mask, _UseUV2Mask)).xz;
    u_xlat8.xy = _Time.yy * vec2(_MaskUSpeed, _MaskVSpeed);
    u_xlat8.xy = fract(u_xlat8.xy);
    u_xlat1.xw = (u_xlatb1.x) ? vs_TEXCOORD2.xy : u_xlat8.xy;
    u_xlat8.xy = (u_xlatb1.z) ? vs_TEXCOORD3.xy : vs_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat8.xy = u_xlat8.xy * _MaskTex_ST.xy + _MaskTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat1.xz = u_xlat1.xw + u_xlat8.xy;
    u_xlat8.xy = u_xlat1.xz;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat8.xy = min(max(u_xlat8.xy, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat8.xy = clamp(u_xlat8.xy, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat8.xy = (-u_xlat1.xz) + u_xlat8.xy;
    u_xlat1.xz = vec2(_ClampUVMaskX, _ClampUVMaskY) * u_xlat8.xy + u_xlat1.xz;
    u_xlat16_20 = texture(_MaskTex, u_xlat1.xz).x;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_20 + (-_MaskIntensity);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_12.x = min(max(u_xlat16_12.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_12.x = clamp(u_xlat16_12.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_22 = (-_MaskIntensity) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_22 = _MaskFeatheredIntensity * u_xlat16_22 + 9.99999975e-05;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_12.x / u_xlat16_22;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_12.x = min(max(u_xlat16_12.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_12.x = clamp(u_xlat16_12.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_2;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb20 = !!(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV2DissolveOffset));
#else
    u_xlatb20 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV2DissolveOffset);
#endif
    u_xlat1.xz = _Time.yy * vec2(_DissolveUSpeed, _DissolveVSpeed);
    u_xlat1.xz = fract(u_xlat1.xz);
    u_xlat1.xz = (bool(u_xlatb20)) ? vs_TEXCOORD2.zw : u_xlat1.xz;
    u_xlat8.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DissolveTex_ST.xy + _DissolveTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat1.xz = u_xlat1.xz + u_xlat8.xy;
    u_xlat8.xy = u_xlat1.xz;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat8.xy = min(max(u_xlat8.xy, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat8.xy = clamp(u_xlat8.xy, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat8.xy = (-u_xlat1.xz) + u_xlat8.xy;
    u_xlat1.xz = vec2(vec2(_ClampUVDissolve, _ClampUVDissolve)) * u_xlat8.xy + u_xlat1.xz;
    u_xlat16_20 = texture(_DissolveTex, u_xlat1.xz).x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb1.x = !!(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV1Dissolve));
#else
    u_xlatb1.x = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV1Dissolve);
#endif
    u_xlat1.x = (u_xlatb1.x) ? vs_TEXCOORD1.z : _DissolveRange;
    u_xlat21 = (-_DissolveEdge) + 1.0;
    u_xlat31 = (-u_xlat1.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat31 = (-u_xlat31) + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat31 = u_xlat16_20 + u_xlat31;
    u_xlat8.x = (-u_xlat21) + _DissolveEdge;
    u_xlat31 = (-u_xlat21) + u_xlat31;
    u_xlat8.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat8.x;
    u_xlat31 = u_xlat31 * u_xlat8.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat31 = min(max(u_xlat31, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat31 = clamp(u_xlat31, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat31 * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat31 = u_xlat31 * u_xlat31;
    u_xlat31 = u_xlat31 * u_xlat18;
    u_xlat16_12.x = _ColorEdgeWidth * 1.39999998 + -0.400000006;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x + (-u_xlat16_12.x);
    u_xlat18 = (-u_xlat1.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x + (-u_xlat18);
    u_xlat20.x = u_xlat16_20 + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat20.x = (-u_xlat21) + u_xlat20.x;
    u_xlat20.x = u_xlat8.x * u_xlat20.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat20.x = min(max(u_xlat20.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat20.x = clamp(u_xlat20.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat20.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat20.x = u_xlat20.x * u_xlat20.x;
    u_xlat20.x = u_xlat20.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat8.xyz = _EdgeColor.xyz * vec3(_EdgeEmission);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat31 * u_xlat16_2;
    u_xlat0.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat0.xyw + (-u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat20.xxx * u_xlat0.xyw + u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat1.x * _Alpha;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_3.w * u_xlat16_2;
    u_xlat16_12.x = (u_xlatb1.y) ? u_xlat16_2 : 1.0;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_12.xxx;
    u_xlat16_12.x = _SrcBlendFactor * _DstBlendFactor;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb30 = !!(u_xlat16_12.x==1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb30 = u_xlat16_12.x==1.0;
#endif
    SV_Target0.w = (u_xlatb30) ? 0.00100000005 : u_xlat16_2;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    return;
}

    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat10_22 + (-_MaskIntensity);
    u_xlat16_24 = clamp(u_xlat16_24, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_35 = (-_MaskIntensity) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_35 = _MaskFeatheredIntensity * u_xlat16_35 + 9.99999975e-05;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_24 / u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat16_24 = clamp(u_xlat16_24, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_13 = u_xlat16_24 * u_xlat16_13;
    u_xlatb22 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV2DissolveOffset);
    u_xlat1.xz = _Time.yy * vec2(_DissolveUSpeed, _DissolveVSpeed);
    u_xlat1.xz = fract(u_xlat1.xz);
    u_xlat1.xz = (bool(u_xlatb22)) ? vs_TEXCOORD2.zw : u_xlat1.xz;
    u_xlat9.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DissolveTex_ST.xy + _DissolveTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat1.xz = u_xlat1.xz + u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat1.xz;
    u_xlat9.xy = clamp(u_xlat9.xy, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat9.xy = (-u_xlat1.xz) + u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat1.xz = vec2(vec2(_ClampUVDissolve, _ClampUVDissolve)) * u_xlat9.xy + u_xlat1.xz;
    u_xlat1.xz = vec2(_AffectDissolveMask) * vec2(u_xlat16_2) + u_xlat1.xz;
    u_xlat10_22 = texture2D(_DissolveTex, u_xlat1.xz).x;
    u_xlatb1.x = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV1Dissolve);
    u_xlat1.x = (u_xlatb1.x) ? vs_TEXCOORD1.z : _DissolveRange;
    u_xlat23 = (-_DissolveEdge) + 1.0;
    u_xlat34 = (-u_xlat1.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat34 = (-u_xlat34) + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat10_22 + u_xlat34;
    u_xlat9.x = (-u_xlat23) + _DissolveEdge;
    u_xlat34 = (-u_xlat23) + u_xlat34;
    u_xlat9.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat9.x;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat34 * u_xlat9.x;
    u_xlat34 = clamp(u_xlat34, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat20 = u_xlat34 * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat34 * u_xlat34;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat34 * u_xlat20;
    u_xlat16_2 = _ColorEdgeWidth * 1.39999998 + -0.400000006;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x + (-u_xlat16_2);
    u_xlat20 = (-u_xlat1.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x + (-u_xlat20);
    u_xlat22.x = u_xlat10_22 + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat22.x = (-u_xlat23) + u_xlat22.x;
    u_xlat22.x = u_xlat9.x * u_xlat22.x;
    u_xlat22.x = clamp(u_xlat22.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat22.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat22.x = u_xlat22.x * u_xlat22.x;
    u_xlat22.x = u_xlat22.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat9.xyz = _EdgeColor.xyz * vec3(_EdgeEmission);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat34 * u_xlat16_13;
    u_xlat0.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat0.xyw + (-u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat22.xxx * u_xlat0.xyw + u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat1.x * _Alpha;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_3.w * u_xlat16_2;
    u_xlat16_13 = (u_xlatb1.y) ? u_xlat16_2 : 1.0;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_13);
    u_xlat16_13 = _SrcBlendFactor * _DstBlendFactor;
    u_xlatb33 = u_xlat16_13==1.0;
    SV_Target0.w = (u_xlatb33) ? 0.00100000005 : u_xlat16_2;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}

UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _DisturbTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
in highp vec4 in_TEXCOORD1;
in highp vec4 in_TEXCOORD2;
in mediump vec4 in_COLOR0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TEXCOORD3;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_COLOR0;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
mediump float u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
bool u_xlatb3;
float u_xlat4;
bool u_xlatb4;
vec2 u_xlat5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
mediump float u_xlat16_6;
bool u_xlatb6;
mediump float u_xlat16_7;
vec2 u_xlat9;
bool u_xlatb10;
vec2 u_xlat12;
float u_xlat15;
bool u_xlatb15;
float u_xlat21;
bool u_xlatb21;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DisturbTex_ST.xy + _DisturbTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat12.xy = _Time.yy * vec2(_DisturbUSpeed, _DisturbVSpeed);
    u_xlat12.xy = fract(u_xlat12.xy);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat12.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_DisturbTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x + -0.5;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb6 = !!(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_DisturbAnimToggle));
#else
    u_xlatb6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_DisturbAnimToggle);
#endif
    u_xlat6.xyz = (bool(u_xlatb6)) ? _DisturbVector.xyz : in_NORMAL0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6 = u_xlat6.x + 0.00100000005;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat0.x * _VertAmplitude;
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat16_6;
    u_xlat16_7 = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_7);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_7);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_1) * u_xlat16_2.xyz + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3];
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3] * u_xlat0.wwww + u_xlat1;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb3 = !!(0.5<_RotateUV);
#else
    u_xlatb3 = 0.5<_RotateUV;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb3){
        u_xlat3.x = _RotateUVAngle * 0.0174532924;
        u_xlat4 = cos(u_xlat3.x);
        u_xlat3.x = sin(u_xlat3.x);
        u_xlat9.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.yx + vec2(-0.5, -0.5);
        u_xlat3.xw = u_xlat9.xy * u_xlat3.xx;
        u_xlat3.x = u_xlat4 * u_xlat9.y + (-u_xlat3.x);
        u_xlat5.x = u_xlat3.x + 0.5;
        u_xlat3.x = u_xlat4 * u_xlat9.x + u_xlat3.w;
        u_xlat5.y = u_xlat3.x + 0.5;
    } else {
        u_xlat5.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    }
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.yzx + _CenterOffset.yzx;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb3 = !!(_Axis<1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb3 = _Axis<1.0;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb3){
        u_xlat3.y = u_xlat1.z;
    } else {
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb15 = !!(_Axis==1.0);
#else
        u_xlatb15 = _Axis==1.0;
#endif
        u_xlat3.xy = (bool(u_xlatb15)) ? u_xlat1.yx : u_xlat1.xy;
        u_xlat1.w = u_xlat3.x;
        u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat1.zw;
    }
    u_xlat15 = min(abs(u_xlat1.x), abs(u_xlat1.y));
    u_xlat21 = max(abs(u_xlat1.x), abs(u_xlat1.y));
    u_xlat21 = float(1.0) / u_xlat21;
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat21 * u_xlat15;
    u_xlat21 = u_xlat15 * u_xlat15;
    u_xlat4 = u_xlat21 * 0.0208350997 + -0.0851330012;
    u_xlat4 = u_xlat21 * u_xlat4 + 0.180141002;
    u_xlat4 = u_xlat21 * u_xlat4 + -0.330299497;
    u_xlat21 = u_xlat21 * u_xlat4 + 0.999866009;
    u_xlat4 = u_xlat21 * u_xlat15;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb10 = !!(abs(u_xlat1.x)<abs(u_xlat1.y));
#else
    u_xlatb10 = abs(u_xlat1.x)<abs(u_xlat1.y);
#endif
    u_xlat4 = u_xlat4 * -2.0 + 1.57079637;
    u_xlat4 = u_xlatb10 ? u_xlat4 : float(0.0);
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat15 * u_xlat21 + u_xlat4;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb21 = !!(u_xlat1.x<(-u_xlat1.x));
#else
    u_xlatb21 = u_xlat1.x<(-u_xlat1.x);
#endif
    u_xlat21 = u_xlatb21 ? -3.14159274 : float(0.0);
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat21 + u_xlat15;
    u_xlat21 = min(u_xlat1.x, u_xlat1.y);
    u_xlat4 = max(u_xlat1.x, u_xlat1.y);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb21 = !!(u_xlat21<(-u_xlat21));
#else
    u_xlatb21 = u_xlat21<(-u_xlat21);
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb4 = !!(u_xlat4>=(-u_xlat4));
#else
    u_xlatb4 = u_xlat4>=(-u_xlat4);
#endif
    u_xlatb21 = u_xlatb21 && u_xlatb4;
    u_xlat15 = (u_xlatb21) ? (-u_xlat15) : u_xlat15;
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat15 * 0.159154937 + 0.5;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat15 + _CenterOffset.w;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb15 = !!(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_CylinderUV));
#else
    u_xlatb15 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_CylinderUV);
#endif
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = (bool(u_xlatb15)) ? u_xlat3.xy : u_xlat5.xy;
    u_xlat3.x = _Zoffset / u_xlat0.w;
    gl_Position.z = u_xlat0.z + (-u_xlat3.x);
    gl_Position.xyw = u_xlat0.xyw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = vec2(0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = in_TEXCOORD1;
    vs_TEXCOORD2 = in_TEXCOORD2;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = in_TEXCOORD3;
    vs_COLOR0 = in_COLOR0;
    return;
}

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MaskFeatheredIntensity;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ClampUVMaskX;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ClampUVMaskY;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _UseUV2Mask;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _UseUV3Mask;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _DissolveTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _DissolveUSpeed;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _DissolveVSpeed;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _DissolveEdge;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _DissolveRange;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _UseUV1Dissolve;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _ClampUVDissolve;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _ColorEdgeWidth;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _EdgeColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _EdgeEmission;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _UseUV2DissolveOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _FresnelColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _FresnelPower;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _FresnelEmission;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _InvertFresnel;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _DisturbVector;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _DisturbTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DisturbUSpeed;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DisturbVSpeed;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DisturbAnimToggle;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _VertAmplitude;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _NoiseTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _MaskTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _DissolveTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD2;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_COLOR0;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec4 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
int u_xlati0;
bool u_xlatb0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
bvec3 u_xlatb1;
mediump float u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
vec2 u_xlat11;
bvec2 u_xlatb11;
mediump float u_xlat16_13;
float u_xlat20;
vec2 u_xlat22;
mediump float u_xlat16_22;
bool u_xlatb22;
float u_xlat23;
mediump float u_xlat16_24;
float u_xlat33;
bool u_xlatb33;
float u_xlat34;
mediump float u_xlat16_35;
void main()
{
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV1));
#else
    u_xlatb0 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV1);
#endif
    u_xlat11.xy = _Time.yy * vec2(_MainUSpeed, _MainVSpeed);
    u_xlat11.xy = fract(u_xlat11.xy);
    u_xlat0.xy = (bool(u_xlatb0)) ? vs_TEXCOORD1.xy : u_xlat11.xy;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb22 = !!(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV3Main));
#else
    u_xlatb22 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV3Main);
#endif
    u_xlat22.xy = (bool(u_xlatb22)) ? vs_TEXCOORD3.xy : vs_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat22.xy = u_xlat22.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy + u_xlat22.xy;
    u_xlat22.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _NoiseTex_ST.xy + _NoiseTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat1.xy = _Time.yy * vec2(_NoiseUSpeed, _NoiseVSpeed);
    u_xlat1.xy = fract(u_xlat1.xy);
    u_xlat22.xy = u_xlat22.xy + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat22.xy;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.xy = min(max(u_xlat1.xy, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.xy = clamp(u_xlat1.xy, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.xy = (-u_xlat22.xy) + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat22.xy = vec2(vec2(_ClampUVNoise, _ClampUVNoise)) * u_xlat1.xy + u_xlat22.xy;
    u_xlat16_22 = texture(_NoiseTex, u_xlat22.xy).x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb33 = !!(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV1Noise));
#else
    u_xlatb33 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV1Noise);
#endif
    u_xlat33 = (u_xlatb33) ? vs_TEXCOORD1.w : _NoiseIntensity;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat33 * u_xlat16_22;
    u_xlat0.xy = vec2(u_xlat16_22) * vec2(u_xlat33) + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat22.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat22.xy = min(max(u_xlat22.xy, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat22.xy = clamp(u_xlat22.xy, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat22.xy = (-u_xlat0.xy) + u_xlat22.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = vec2(_ClampUVMainX, _ClampUVMainY) * u_xlat22.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, u_xlat0.xy);
    u_xlatb1.xy = notEqual(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0), vec4(_RAlpha, _IF_ADD_MODE, _RAlpha, _RAlpha)).xy;
    u_xlat16_13 = (u_xlatb1.x) ? u_xlat16_0.x : u_xlat16_0.w;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = _ColorBlack.xyz * vec3(_EmissionBlack);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = _ColorLight.xyz * vec3(_EmissionLight);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb33 = !!(0.5<_UseThreeColor);
#else
    u_xlatb33 = 0.5<_UseThreeColor;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb33){
        u_xlat16_5.xyz = _ColorMiddle.xyz * vec3(_EmissionMiddle);
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = min(max(u_xlat16_6.xyz, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = clamp(u_xlat16_6.xyz, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_7.xyz = _ColorMiddle.xyz * vec3(_EmissionMiddle) + (-u_xlat16_3.xyz);
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
        u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + vec3(-0.5, -0.5, -0.5);
        u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_7.xyz = min(max(u_xlat16_7.xyz, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_7.xyz = clamp(u_xlat16_7.xyz, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_8.xyz = _ColorLight.xyz * vec3(_EmissionLight) + (-u_xlat16_5.xyz);
        u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
        u_xlat16_5.xyz = (-u_xlat16_6.xyz) + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
        u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    } else {
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = _ColorLight.xyz * vec3(_EmissionLight) + (-u_xlat16_3.xyz);
        u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    }
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb33 = !!(unity_WorldTransformParams.w<0.0);
#else
    u_xlatb33 = unity_WorldTransformParams.w<0.0;
#endif
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = (uint((gl_FrontFacing ? 0xffffffffu : uint(0))) != uint(0)) ? u_xlat16_3.xyz : u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = (uint((gl_FrontFacing ? 0xffffffffu : uint(0))) != uint(0)) ? u_xlat16_4.xyz : u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = (bool(u_xlatb33)) ? u_xlat16_4.xyz : u_xlat16_3.xyz;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(_CullMode<0.5);
#else
    u_xlatb0 = _CullMode<0.5;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb11.x = !!(0.5<_TwoFace);
#else
    u_xlatb11.x = 0.5<_TwoFace;
#endif
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlatb0 && u_xlatb11.x;
    u_xlati0 = u_xlatb0 ? 1 : int(0);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = (int(u_xlati0) != 0) ? u_xlat16_3.xyz : u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = _Time.y * _ColorFrequency;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 0.00318471342;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb11.x = !!(u_xlat0.x>=(-u_xlat0.x));
#else
    u_xlatb11.x = u_xlat0.x>=(-u_xlat0.x);
#endif
    u_xlat0.x = fract(abs(u_xlat0.x));
    u_xlat0.x = (u_xlatb11.x) ? u_xlat0.x : (-u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 314.0;
    u_xlat0.x = sin(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlatb11.xy = notEqual(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0), vec4(_IsLerpColor, _NoVertexColor, _IsLerpColor, _IsLerpColor)).xy;
    u_xlat1.xzw = (-u_xlat16_3.xyz) + _ColorLerp.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xzw = abs(u_xlat0.xxx) * u_xlat1.xzw + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (u_xlatb11.x) ? u_xlat1.xzw : u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3 = (u_xlatb11.y) ? vec4(1.0, 1.0, 1.0, 1.0) : vs_COLOR0;
    u_xlatb1.xz = notEqual(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0), vec4(_UseUV2Mask, _UseUV2Mask, _UseUV3Mask, _UseUV2Mask)).xz;
    u_xlat9.xy = _Time.yy * vec2(_MaskUSpeed, _MaskVSpeed);
    u_xlat9.xy = fract(u_xlat9.xy);
    u_xlat1.xw = (u_xlatb1.x) ? vs_TEXCOORD2.xy : u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat9.xy = (u_xlatb1.z) ? vs_TEXCOORD3.xy : vs_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xy * _MaskTex_ST.xy + _MaskTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat1.xz = u_xlat1.xw + u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat1.xz;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat9.xy = min(max(u_xlat9.xy, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat9.xy = clamp(u_xlat9.xy, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat9.xy = (-u_xlat1.xz) + u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat1.xz = vec2(_ClampUVMaskX, _ClampUVMaskY) * u_xlat9.xy + u_xlat1.xz;
    u_xlat1.xz = vec2(_AffectDissolveMask) * vec2(u_xlat16_2) + u_xlat1.xz;
    u_xlat16_22 = texture(_MaskTex, u_xlat1.xz).x;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_22 + (-_MaskIntensity);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_24 = min(max(u_xlat16_24, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_24 = clamp(u_xlat16_24, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_35 = (-_MaskIntensity) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_35 = _MaskFeatheredIntensity * u_xlat16_35 + 9.99999975e-05;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_24 / u_xlat16_35;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_24 = min(max(u_xlat16_24, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_24 = clamp(u_xlat16_24, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_13 = u_xlat16_24 * u_xlat16_13;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb22 = !!(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV2DissolveOffset));
#else
    u_xlatb22 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV2DissolveOffset);
#endif
    u_xlat1.xz = _Time.yy * vec2(_DissolveUSpeed, _DissolveVSpeed);
    u_xlat1.xz = fract(u_xlat1.xz);
    u_xlat1.xz = (bool(u_xlatb22)) ? vs_TEXCOORD2.zw : u_xlat1.xz;
    u_xlat9.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DissolveTex_ST.xy + _DissolveTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat1.xz = u_xlat1.xz + u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat1.xz;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat9.xy = min(max(u_xlat9.xy, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat9.xy = clamp(u_xlat9.xy, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat9.xy = (-u_xlat1.xz) + u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat1.xz = vec2(vec2(_ClampUVDissolve, _ClampUVDissolve)) * u_xlat9.xy + u_xlat1.xz;
    u_xlat1.xz = vec2(_AffectDissolveMask) * vec2(u_xlat16_2) + u_xlat1.xz;
    u_xlat16_22 = texture(_DissolveTex, u_xlat1.xz).x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb1.x = !!(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV1Dissolve));
#else
    u_xlatb1.x = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV1Dissolve);
#endif
    u_xlat1.x = (u_xlatb1.x) ? vs_TEXCOORD1.z : _DissolveRange;
    u_xlat23 = (-_DissolveEdge) + 1.0;
    u_xlat34 = (-u_xlat1.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat34 = (-u_xlat34) + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat16_22 + u_xlat34;
    u_xlat9.x = (-u_xlat23) + _DissolveEdge;
    u_xlat34 = (-u_xlat23) + u_xlat34;
    u_xlat9.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat9.x;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat34 * u_xlat9.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat34 = min(max(u_xlat34, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat34 = clamp(u_xlat34, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat20 = u_xlat34 * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat34 * u_xlat34;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat34 * u_xlat20;
    u_xlat16_2 = _ColorEdgeWidth * 1.39999998 + -0.400000006;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x + (-u_xlat16_2);
    u_xlat20 = (-u_xlat1.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x + (-u_xlat20);
    u_xlat22.x = u_xlat16_22 + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat22.x = (-u_xlat23) + u_xlat22.x;
    u_xlat22.x = u_xlat9.x * u_xlat22.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat22.x = min(max(u_xlat22.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat22.x = clamp(u_xlat22.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat22.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat22.x = u_xlat22.x * u_xlat22.x;
    u_xlat22.x = u_xlat22.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat9.xyz = _EdgeColor.xyz * vec3(_EdgeEmission);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat34 * u_xlat16_13;
    u_xlat0.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat0.xyw + (-u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat22.xxx * u_xlat0.xyw + u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat1.x * _Alpha;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_3.w * u_xlat16_2;
    u_xlat16_13 = (u_xlatb1.y) ? u_xlat16_2 : 1.0;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_13);
    u_xlat16_13 = _SrcBlendFactor * _DstBlendFactor;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb33 = !!(u_xlat16_13==1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb33 = u_xlat16_13==1.0;
#endif
    SV_Target0.w = (u_xlatb33) ? 0.00100000005 : u_xlat16_2;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}
SubProgram "gles " {
Local Keywords { "_FRESNEL_ON" "_VERTEXDISTURB_ON" }
"// hash: c5ef07418e06336f
#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec4 _Time;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
uniform 	mediump float _Zoffset;
uniform 	mediump float _RotateUV;
uniform 	mediump float _RotateUVAngle;
uniform 	mediump float _CylinderUV;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _CenterOffset;
uniform 	mediump float _Axis;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _DisturbVector;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _DisturbTex_ST;
uniform 	mediump float _DisturbUSpeed;
uniform 	mediump float _DisturbVSpeed;
uniform 	mediump float _DisturbAnimToggle;
uniform 	mediump float _VertAmplitude;
uniform lowp sampler2D _DisturbTex;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TEXCOORD1;
attribute highp vec4 in_TEXCOORD2;
attribute mediump vec4 in_COLOR0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TEXCOORD3;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD2;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_COLOR0;
varying highp vec3 vs_NORMAL0;
varying highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD4;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
mediump float u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
bool u_xlatb3;
float u_xlat4;
bool u_xlatb4;
vec2 u_xlat5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
mediump float u_xlat16_6;
bool u_xlatb6;
mediump float u_xlat16_7;
vec2 u_xlat9;
bool u_xlatb10;
vec2 u_xlat12;
float u_xlat15;
bool u_xlatb15;
float u_xlat21;
bool u_xlatb21;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DisturbTex_ST.xy + _DisturbTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat12.xy = _Time.yy * vec2(_DisturbUSpeed, _DisturbVSpeed);
    u_xlat12.xy = fract(u_xlat12.xy);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat12.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = texture2DLod(_DisturbTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x + -0.5;
    u_xlatb6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_DisturbAnimToggle);
    u_xlat6.xyz = (bool(u_xlatb6)) ? _DisturbVector.xyz : in_NORMAL0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6 = u_xlat6.x + 0.00100000005;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat0.x * _VertAmplitude;
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat16_6;
    u_xlat16_7 = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_7);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_7);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_1) * u_xlat16_2.xyz + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3];
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3] * u_xlat0.wwww + u_xlat1;
    u_xlatb3 = 0.5<_RotateUV;
    if(u_xlatb3){
        u_xlat3.x = _RotateUVAngle * 0.0174532924;
        u_xlat4 = cos(u_xlat3.x);
        u_xlat3.x = sin(u_xlat3.x);
        u_xlat9.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.yx + vec2(-0.5, -0.5);
        u_xlat3.xw = u_xlat9.xy * u_xlat3.xx;
        u_xlat3.x = u_xlat4 * u_xlat9.y + (-u_xlat3.x);
        u_xlat5.x = u_xlat3.x + 0.5;
        u_xlat3.x = u_xlat4 * u_xlat9.x + u_xlat3.w;
        u_xlat5.y = u_xlat3.x + 0.5;
    } else {
        u_xlat5.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    }
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.yzx + _CenterOffset.yzx;
    u_xlatb3 = _Axis<1.0;
    if(u_xlatb3){
        u_xlat3.y = u_xlat1.z;
    } else {
        u_xlatb15 = _Axis==1.0;
        u_xlat3.xy = (bool(u_xlatb15)) ? u_xlat1.yx : u_xlat1.xy;
        u_xlat1.w = u_xlat3.x;
        u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat1.zw;
    }
    u_xlat15 = min(abs(u_xlat1.x), abs(u_xlat1.y));
    u_xlat21 = max(abs(u_xlat1.x), abs(u_xlat1.y));
    u_xlat21 = float(1.0) / u_xlat21;
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat21 * u_xlat15;
    u_xlat21 = u_xlat15 * u_xlat15;
    u_xlat4 = u_xlat21 * 0.0208350997 + -0.0851330012;
    u_xlat4 = u_xlat21 * u_xlat4 + 0.180141002;
    u_xlat4 = u_xlat21 * u_xlat4 + -0.330299497;
    u_xlat21 = u_xlat21 * u_xlat4 + 0.999866009;
    u_xlat4 = u_xlat21 * u_xlat15;
    u_xlatb10 = abs(u_xlat1.x)<abs(u_xlat1.y);
    u_xlat4 = u_xlat4 * -2.0 + 1.57079637;
    u_xlat4 = u_xlatb10 ? u_xlat4 : float(0.0);
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat15 * u_xlat21 + u_xlat4;
    u_xlatb21 = u_xlat1.x<(-u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat21 = u_xlatb21 ? -3.14159274 : float(0.0);
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat21 + u_xlat15;
    u_xlat21 = min(u_xlat1.x, u_xlat1.y);
    u_xlat4 = max(u_xlat1.x, u_xlat1.y);
    u_xlatb21 = u_xlat21<(-u_xlat21);
    u_xlatb4 = u_xlat4>=(-u_xlat4);
    u_xlatb21 = u_xlatb21 && u_xlatb4;
    u_xlat15 = (u_xlatb21) ? (-u_xlat15) : u_xlat15;
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat15 * 0.159154937 + 0.5;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat15 + _CenterOffset.w;
    u_xlatb15 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_CylinderUV);
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = (bool(u_xlatb15)) ? u_xlat3.xy : u_xlat5.xy;
    u_xlat3.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat3.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat21 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat21 = max(u_xlat21, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat21 = inversesqrt(u_xlat21);
    vs_NORMAL0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat21) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.x = _Zoffset / u_xlat0.w;
    gl_Position.z = u_xlat0.z + (-u_xlat3.x);
    gl_Position.xyw = u_xlat0.xyw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = vec2(0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = in_TEXCOORD1;
    vs_TEXCOORD2 = in_TEXCOORD2;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = in_TEXCOORD3;
    vs_COLOR0 = in_COLOR0;
    return;
}

#define SV_Target0 gl_FragData[0]
vec4 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
lowp vec4 u_xlat10_0;
bool u_xlatb0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
int u_xlati1;
bvec2 u_xlatb1;
mediump float u_xlat16_2;

mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_7;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_10;
vec2 u_xlat11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
mediump float u_xlat16_15;

bool u_xlatb22;
bvec2 u_xlatb23;
bool u_xlatb33;
bool u_xlatb34;
float u_xlat42;
void main()
{
    u_xlatb0 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV1);
    u_xlat11.xy = _Time.yy * vec2(_MainUSpeed, _MainVSpeed);
    u_xlat11.xy = fract(u_xlat11.xy);
    u_xlat0.xy = (bool(u_xlatb0)) ? vs_TEXCOORD1.xy : u_xlat11.xy;
    u_xlatb22 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV3Main);
    u_xlat22.xy = (bool(u_xlatb22)) ? vs_TEXCOORD3.xy : vs_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat22.xy = u_xlat22.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy + u_xlat22.xy;
    u_xlat22.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat22.xy = clamp(u_xlat22.xy, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat22.xy = (-u_xlat0.xy) + u_xlat22.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = vec2(_ClampUVMainX, _ClampUVMainY) * u_xlat22.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat10_0 = texture2D(_MainTex, u_xlat0.xy);
    u_xlatb1.xy = notEqual(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0), vec4(_RAlpha, _IF_ADD_MODE, _RAlpha, _RAlpha)).xy;
    u_xlat16_2 = (u_xlatb1.x) ? u_xlat10_0.x : u_xlat10_0.w;
    u_xlat16_3 = _ColorBlack * vec4(_EmissionBlack);
    u_xlat16_4 = _ColorLight * vec4(_EmissionLight);
    u_xlatb33 = 0.5<_UseThreeColor;
    if(u_xlatb33){
        u_xlat16_5 = _ColorMiddle * vec4(_EmissionMiddle);
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz + u_xlat10_0.xyz;
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = clamp(u_xlat16_6.xyz, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_6.w = u_xlat16_2 + u_xlat16_2;
        u_xlat16_6.w = clamp(u_xlat16_6.w, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_7 = _ColorMiddle * vec4(_EmissionMiddle) + (-u_xlat16_3);
        u_xlat16_6 = u_xlat16_6 * u_xlat16_7 + u_xlat16_3;
        u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz + vec3(-0.5, -0.5, -0.5);
        u_xlat16_7.w = u_xlat16_2 + -0.5;
        u_xlat16_7 = u_xlat16_7 + u_xlat16_7;
        u_xlat16_7 = clamp(u_xlat16_7, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_8 = _ColorLight * vec4(_EmissionLight) + (-u_xlat16_5);
        u_xlat16_5 = u_xlat16_7 * u_xlat16_8 + u_xlat16_5;
        u_xlat16_5 = (-u_xlat16_6) + u_xlat16_5;
        u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
        u_xlat16_7.w = u_xlat16_2 * u_xlat16_5.w;
        u_xlat16_5 = u_xlat16_6 + u_xlat16_7;
    } else {
        u_xlat16_6 = _ColorLight * vec4(_EmissionLight) + (-u_xlat16_3);
        u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
        u_xlat16_7.w = u_xlat16_2 * u_xlat16_6.w;
        u_xlat16_5 = _ColorBlack * vec4(_EmissionBlack) + u_xlat16_7;
    }
    u_xlatb33 = unity_WorldTransformParams.w<0.0;
    u_xlat16_10 = (int((gl_FrontFacing ? 1 : 0)) != 0) ? u_xlat16_3 : u_xlat16_4;
    u_xlat16_4 = (int((gl_FrontFacing ? 1 : 0)) != 0) ? u_xlat16_4 : u_xlat16_3;
    u_xlat16_3 = u_xlat16_10;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.w = u_xlat16_2 * u_xlat16_4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.w = u_xlat16_2 * u_xlat16_3.w;
    u_xlat16_0 = (bool(u_xlatb33)) ? u_xlat16_6 : u_xlat16_4;
    u_xlatb1.x = _CullMode<0.5;
    u_xlatb23.x = 0.5<_TwoFace;
    u_xlatb1.x = u_xlatb1.x && u_xlatb23.x;
    u_xlati1 = u_xlatb1.x ? 1 : int(0);
    u_xlat16_0 = (int(u_xlati1) != 0) ? u_xlat16_0 : u_xlat16_5;
    u_xlat1.x = _Time.y * _ColorFrequency;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.00318471342;
    u_xlatb23.x = u_xlat1.x>=(-u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.x = fract(abs(u_xlat1.x));
    u_xlat1.x = (u_xlatb23.x) ? u_xlat1.x : (-u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 314.0;
    u_xlat1.x = sin(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlatb23.xy = notEqual(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0), vec4(_IsLerpColor, _NoVertexColor, _IsLerpColor, _NoVertexColor)).xy;
    u_xlat3 = (-u_xlat16_0) + _ColorLerp;
    u_xlat3 = abs(u_xlat1.xxxx) * u_xlat3 + u_xlat16_0;
    u_xlat0 = (u_xlatb23.x) ? u_xlat3 : u_xlat16_0;
    u_xlat16_3 = (u_xlatb23.y) ? vec4(1.0, 1.0, 1.0, 1.0) : vs_COLOR0;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(vs_NORMAL0.xyz, vs_NORMAL0.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat1.xxx * vs_NORMAL0.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat42 = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat42 = inversesqrt(u_xlat42);
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat42) * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat1.xzw, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat1.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_13.x = max(_FresnelPower, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.x = log2(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat1.x = exp2(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * _FresnelColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * vec3(vec3(_FresnelEmission, _FresnelEmission, _FresnelEmission));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat0.w * u_xlat16_2;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat1.x * _FresnelEmission;
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_15 = _FresnelColor.w * _InvertFresnel + (-u_xlat16_2);
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_15 + u_xlat16_2;
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat0.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_2 * _Alpha;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_3.w * u_xlat16_2;
    u_xlat16_13.x = (u_xlatb1.y) ? u_xlat16_2 : 1.0;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xzw * u_xlat16_13.xxx;
    u_xlat16_13.x = _SrcBlendFactor * _DstBlendFactor;
    u_xlatb34 = u_xlat16_13.x==1.0;
    SV_Target0.w = (u_xlatb34) ? 0.00100000005 : u_xlat16_2;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz;
    return;
}

{
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DisturbTex_ST.xy + _DisturbTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat12.xy = _Time.yy * vec2(_DisturbUSpeed, _DisturbVSpeed);
    u_xlat12.xy = fract(u_xlat12.xy);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat12.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_DisturbTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x + -0.5;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb6 = !!(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_DisturbAnimToggle));
#else
    u_xlatb6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_DisturbAnimToggle);
#endif
    u_xlat6.xyz = (bool(u_xlatb6)) ? _DisturbVector.xyz : in_NORMAL0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6 = u_xlat6.x + 0.00100000005;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat0.x * _VertAmplitude;
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat16_6;
    u_xlat16_7 = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_7);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_7);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_1) * u_xlat16_2.xyz + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3];
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3] * u_xlat0.wwww + u_xlat1;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb3 = !!(0.5<_RotateUV);
#else
    u_xlatb3 = 0.5<_RotateUV;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb3){
        u_xlat3.x = _RotateUVAngle * 0.0174532924;
        u_xlat4 = cos(u_xlat3.x);
        u_xlat3.x = sin(u_xlat3.x);
        u_xlat9.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.yx + vec2(-0.5, -0.5);
        u_xlat3.xw = u_xlat9.xy * u_xlat3.xx;
        u_xlat3.x = u_xlat4 * u_xlat9.y + (-u_xlat3.x);
        u_xlat5.x = u_xlat3.x + 0.5;
        u_xlat3.x = u_xlat4 * u_xlat9.x + u_xlat3.w;
        u_xlat5.y = u_xlat3.x + 0.5;
    } else {
        u_xlat5.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    }
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.yzx + _CenterOffset.yzx;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb3 = !!(_Axis<1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb3 = _Axis<1.0;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb3){
        u_xlat3.y = u_xlat1.z;
    } else {
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb15 = !!(_Axis==1.0);
#else
        u_xlatb15 = _Axis==1.0;
#endif
        u_xlat3.xy = (bool(u_xlatb15)) ? u_xlat1.yx : u_xlat1.xy;
        u_xlat1.w = u_xlat3.x;
        u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat1.zw;
    }
    u_xlat15 = min(abs(u_xlat1.x), abs(u_xlat1.y));
    u_xlat21 = max(abs(u_xlat1.x), abs(u_xlat1.y));
    u_xlat21 = float(1.0) / u_xlat21;
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat21 * u_xlat15;
    u_xlat21 = u_xlat15 * u_xlat15;
    u_xlat4 = u_xlat21 * 0.0208350997 + -0.0851330012;
    u_xlat4 = u_xlat21 * u_xlat4 + 0.180141002;
    u_xlat4 = u_xlat21 * u_xlat4 + -0.330299497;
    u_xlat21 = u_xlat21 * u_xlat4 + 0.999866009;
    u_xlat4 = u_xlat21 * u_xlat15;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb10 = !!(abs(u_xlat1.x)<abs(u_xlat1.y));
#else
    u_xlatb10 = abs(u_xlat1.x)<abs(u_xlat1.y);
#endif
    u_xlat4 = u_xlat4 * -2.0 + 1.57079637;
    u_xlat4 = u_xlatb10 ? u_xlat4 : float(0.0);
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat15 * u_xlat21 + u_xlat4;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb21 = !!(u_xlat1.x<(-u_xlat1.x));
#else
    u_xlatb21 = u_xlat1.x<(-u_xlat1.x);
#endif
    u_xlat21 = u_xlatb21 ? -3.14159274 : float(0.0);
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat21 + u_xlat15;
    u_xlat21 = min(u_xlat1.x, u_xlat1.y);
    u_xlat4 = max(u_xlat1.x, u_xlat1.y);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb21 = !!(u_xlat21<(-u_xlat21));
#else
    u_xlatb21 = u_xlat21<(-u_xlat21);
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb4 = !!(u_xlat4>=(-u_xlat4));
#else
    u_xlatb4 = u_xlat4>=(-u_xlat4);
#endif
    u_xlatb21 = u_xlatb21 && u_xlatb4;
    u_xlat15 = (u_xlatb21) ? (-u_xlat15) : u_xlat15;
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat15 * 0.159154937 + 0.5;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat15 + _CenterOffset.w;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb15 = !!(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_CylinderUV));
#else
    u_xlatb15 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_CylinderUV);
#endif
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = (bool(u_xlatb15)) ? u_xlat3.xy : u_xlat5.xy;
    u_xlat3.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat3.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat21 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat21 = max(u_xlat21, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat21 = inversesqrt(u_xlat21);
    vs_NORMAL0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat21) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.x = _Zoffset / u_xlat0.w;
    gl_Position.z = u_xlat0.z + (-u_xlat3.x);
    gl_Position.xyw = u_xlat0.xyw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = vec2(0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = in_TEXCOORD1;
    vs_TEXCOORD2 = in_TEXCOORD2;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = in_TEXCOORD3;
    vs_COLOR0 = in_COLOR0;
    return;
}

#endif

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MaskFeatheredIntensity;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ClampUVMaskY;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _UseUV2Mask;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _UseUV3Mask;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _DissolveTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _DissolveUSpeed;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _DissolveVSpeed;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _DissolveEdge;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _DissolveRange;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _UseUV1Dissolve;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _ClampUVDissolve;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _ColorEdgeWidth;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _EdgeColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _EdgeEmission;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _UseUV2DissolveOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _FresnelColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _FresnelPower;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _FresnelEmission;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _InvertFresnel;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _DisturbVector;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _DisturbTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DisturbUSpeed;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DisturbVSpeed;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DisturbAnimToggle;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _VertAmplitude;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_COLOR0;
in highp vec3 vs_NORMAL0;
in highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD4;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec4 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
bool u_xlatb0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
int u_xlati1;
bvec2 u_xlatb1;
mediump float u_xlat16_2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_7;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_10;
vec2 u_xlat11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
mediump float u_xlat16_15;
vec2 u_xlat22;
bool u_xlatb22;
bvec2 u_xlatb23;
bool u_xlatb33;
bool u_xlatb34;
float u_xlat42;
void main()
{
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV1));
#else
    u_xlatb0 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV1);
#endif
    u_xlat11.xy = _Time.yy * vec2(_MainUSpeed, _MainVSpeed);
    u_xlat11.xy = fract(u_xlat11.xy);
    u_xlat0.xy = (bool(u_xlatb0)) ? vs_TEXCOORD1.xy : u_xlat11.xy;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb22 = !!(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV3Main));
#else
    u_xlatb22 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV3Main);
#endif
    u_xlat22.xy = (bool(u_xlatb22)) ? vs_TEXCOORD3.xy : vs_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat22.xy = u_xlat22.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy + u_xlat22.xy;
    u_xlat22.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat22.xy = min(max(u_xlat22.xy, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat22.xy = clamp(u_xlat22.xy, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat22.xy = (-u_xlat0.xy) + u_xlat22.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = vec2(_ClampUVMainX, _ClampUVMainY) * u_xlat22.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, u_xlat0.xy);
    u_xlatb1.xy = notEqual(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0), vec4(_RAlpha, _IF_ADD_MODE, _RAlpha, _RAlpha)).xy;
    u_xlat16_2 = (u_xlatb1.x) ? u_xlat16_0.x : u_xlat16_0.w;
    u_xlat16_3 = _ColorBlack * vec4(_EmissionBlack);
    u_xlat16_4 = _ColorLight * vec4(_EmissionLight);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb33 = !!(0.5<_UseThreeColor);
#else
    u_xlatb33 = 0.5<_UseThreeColor;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb33){
        u_xlat16_5 = _ColorMiddle * vec4(_EmissionMiddle);
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = min(max(u_xlat16_6.xyz, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = clamp(u_xlat16_6.xyz, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_6.w = u_xlat16_2 + u_xlat16_2;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_6.w = min(max(u_xlat16_6.w, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_6.w = clamp(u_xlat16_6.w, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_7 = _ColorMiddle * vec4(_EmissionMiddle) + (-u_xlat16_3);
        u_xlat16_6 = u_xlat16_6 * u_xlat16_7 + u_xlat16_3;
        u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + vec3(-0.5, -0.5, -0.5);
        u_xlat16_7.w = u_xlat16_2 + -0.5;
        u_xlat16_7 = u_xlat16_7 + u_xlat16_7;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_7 = min(max(u_xlat16_7, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_7 = clamp(u_xlat16_7, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_8 = _ColorLight * vec4(_EmissionLight) + (-u_xlat16_5);
        u_xlat16_5 = u_xlat16_7 * u_xlat16_8 + u_xlat16_5;
        u_xlat16_5 = (-u_xlat16_6) + u_xlat16_5;
        u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
        u_xlat16_7.w = u_xlat16_2 * u_xlat16_5.w;
        u_xlat16_5 = u_xlat16_6 + u_xlat16_7;
    } else {
        u_xlat16_6 = _ColorLight * vec4(_EmissionLight) + (-u_xlat16_3);
        u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
        u_xlat16_7.w = u_xlat16_2 * u_xlat16_6.w;
        u_xlat16_5 = _ColorBlack * vec4(_EmissionBlack) + u_xlat16_7;
    }
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb33 = !!(unity_WorldTransformParams.w<0.0);
#else
    u_xlatb33 = unity_WorldTransformParams.w<0.0;
#endif
    u_xlat16_10 = (uint((gl_FrontFacing ? 0xffffffffu : uint(0))) != uint(0)) ? u_xlat16_3 : u_xlat16_4;
    u_xlat16_4 = (uint((gl_FrontFacing ? 0xffffffffu : uint(0))) != uint(0)) ? u_xlat16_4 : u_xlat16_3;
    u_xlat16_3 = u_xlat16_10;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.w = u_xlat16_2 * u_xlat16_4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.w = u_xlat16_2 * u_xlat16_3.w;
    u_xlat16_0 = (bool(u_xlatb33)) ? u_xlat16_6 : u_xlat16_4;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb1.x = !!(_CullMode<0.5);
#else
    u_xlatb1.x = _CullMode<0.5;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb23.x = !!(0.5<_TwoFace);
#else
    u_xlatb23.x = 0.5<_TwoFace;
#endif
    u_xlatb1.x = u_xlatb1.x && u_xlatb23.x;
    u_xlati1 = u_xlatb1.x ? 1 : int(0);
    u_xlat16_0 = (int(u_xlati1) != 0) ? u_xlat16_0 : u_xlat16_5;
    u_xlat1.x = _Time.y * _ColorFrequency;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.00318471342;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb23.x = !!(u_xlat1.x>=(-u_xlat1.x));
#else
    u_xlatb23.x = u_xlat1.x>=(-u_xlat1.x);
#endif
    u_xlat1.x = fract(abs(u_xlat1.x));
    u_xlat1.x = (u_xlatb23.x) ? u_xlat1.x : (-u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 314.0;
    u_xlat1.x = sin(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlatb23.xy = notEqual(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0), vec4(_IsLerpColor, _NoVertexColor, _IsLerpColor, _NoVertexColor)).xy;
    u_xlat3 = (-u_xlat16_0) + _ColorLerp;
    u_xlat3 = abs(u_xlat1.xxxx) * u_xlat3 + u_xlat16_0;
    u_xlat0 = (u_xlatb23.x) ? u_xlat3 : u_xlat16_0;
    u_xlat16_3 = (u_xlatb23.y) ? vec4(1.0, 1.0, 1.0, 1.0) : vs_COLOR0;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(vs_NORMAL0.xyz, vs_NORMAL0.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat1.xxx * vs_NORMAL0.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat42 = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat42 = inversesqrt(u_xlat42);
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat42) * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat1.xzw, u_xlat9.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.x = min(max(u_xlat1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat1.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_13.x = max(_FresnelPower, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.x = log2(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat1.x = exp2(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * _FresnelColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * vec3(vec3(_FresnelEmission, _FresnelEmission, _FresnelEmission));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat0.w * u_xlat16_2;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat1.x * _FresnelEmission;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_15 = _FresnelColor.w * _InvertFresnel + (-u_xlat16_2);
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_15 + u_xlat16_2;
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat0.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_2 * _Alpha;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_3.w * u_xlat16_2;
    u_xlat16_13.x = (u_xlatb1.y) ? u_xlat16_2 : 1.0;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xzw * u_xlat16_13.xxx;
    u_xlat16_13.x = _SrcBlendFactor * _DstBlendFactor;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb34 = !!(u_xlat16_13.x==1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb34 = u_xlat16_13.x==1.0;
#endif
    SV_Target0.w = (u_xlatb34) ? 0.00100000005 : u_xlat16_2;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz;
    return;
}

    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat0.w * u_xlat16_2;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat1.x * _FresnelEmission;
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_16 = _FresnelColor.w * _InvertFresnel + (-u_xlat16_2);
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_16 + u_xlat16_2;
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat0.xyz + u_xlat16_14.xyz;
    u_xlatb9.xy = notEqual(vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0), vec4(_UseUV2Mask, _UseUV3Mask, _UseUV2Mask, _UseUV2Mask)).xy;
    u_xlat33.xy = _Time.yy * vec2(_MaskUSpeed, _MaskVSpeed);
    u_xlat33.xy = fract(u_xlat33.xy);
    u_xlat9.xz = (u_xlatb9.x) ? vs_TEXCOORD2.xy : u_xlat33.xy;
    u_xlat21.xz = (u_xlatb9.y) ? vs_TEXCOORD3.xy : vs_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat21.xz = u_xlat21.xz * _MaskTex_ST.xy + _MaskTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xz + u_xlat21.xz;
    u_xlat33.xy = u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat33.xy = clamp(u_xlat33.xy, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat33.xy = (-u_xlat9.xy) + u_xlat33.xy;
    u_xlat9.xy = vec2(_ClampUVMaskX, _ClampUVMaskY) * u_xlat33.xy + u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat10_9 = texture2D(_MaskTex, u_xlat9.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat10_9 + (-_MaskIntensity);
    u_xlat16_14.x = clamp(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_26 = (-_MaskIntensity) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_26 = _MaskFeatheredIntensity * u_xlat16_26 + 9.99999975e-05;
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat16_14.x / u_xlat16_26;
    u_xlat16_14.x = clamp(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_14.x * u_xlat16_2;
    u_xlatb9.x = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV2DissolveOffset);
    u_xlat21.xy = _Time.yy * vec2(_DissolveUSpeed, _DissolveVSpeed);
    u_xlat21.xy = fract(u_xlat21.xy);
    u_xlat9.xy = (u_xlatb9.x) ? vs_TEXCOORD2.zw : u_xlat21.xy;
    u_xlat33.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DissolveTex_ST.xy + _DissolveTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xy + u_xlat33.xy;
    u_xlat33.xy = u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat33.xy = clamp(u_xlat33.xy, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat33.xy = (-u_xlat9.xy) + u_xlat33.xy;
    u_xlat9.xy = vec2(vec2(_ClampUVDissolve, _ClampUVDissolve)) * u_xlat33.xy + u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat10_9 = texture2D(_DissolveTex, u_xlat9.xy).x;
    u_xlatb21 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0)!=vec4(_UseUV1Dissolve);
    u_xlat21.x = (u_xlatb21) ? vs_TEXCOORD1.z : _DissolveRange;
    u_xlat33.x = (-_DissolveEdge) + 1.0;
    u_xlat45 = (-u_xlat21.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat45 = (-u_xlat45) + u_xlat21.x;
    u_xlat45 = u_xlat45 + u_xlat10_9;
    u_xlat10.x = (-u_xlat33.x) + _DissolveEdge;
    u_xlat45 = (-u_xlat33.x) + u_xlat45;
    u_xlat10.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat10.x;
    u_xlat45 = u_xlat45 * u_xlat10.x;
    u_xlat45 = clamp(u_xlat45, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat22 = u_xlat45 * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat45 = u_xlat45 * u_xlat45;
    u_xlat45 = u_xlat45 * u_xlat22;
    u_xlat16_14.x = _ColorEdgeWidth * 1.39999998 + -0.400000006;
    u_xlat21.x = (-u_xlat16_14.x) + u_xlat21.x;
    u_xlat22 = (-u_xlat21.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat21.x = u_xlat21.x + (-u_xlat22);
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat10_9 + u_xlat21.x;
    u_xlat9.x = (-u_xlat33.x) + u_xlat9.x;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat10.x * u_xlat9.x;
    u_xlat9.x = clamp(u_xlat9.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat21.x = u_xlat9.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat9.x * u_xlat9.x;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat9.x * u_xlat21.x;
    u_xlat10.xyz = _EdgeColor.xyz * vec3(_EdgeEmission);
    u_xlat21.x = u_xlat16_2 * u_xlat45;
    u_xlat1.xzw = (-_EdgeColor.xyz) * vec3(_EdgeEmission) + u_xlat1.xzw;
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat9.xxx * u_xlat1.xzw + u_xlat10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat21.x * _Alpha;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_3.w * u_xlat16_2;
    u_xlat16_14.x = (u_xlatb1.y) ? u_xlat16_2 : 1.0;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xzw * u_xlat16_14.xxx;
    u_xlat16_14.x = _SrcBlendFactor * _DstBlendFactor;
    u_xlatb37 = u_xlat16_14.x==1.0;
    SV_Target0.w = (u_xlatb37) ? 0.00100000005 : u_xlat16_2;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}

UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _DisturbTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
in highp vec4 in_TEXCOORD1;
in highp vec4 in_TEXCOORD2;
in mediump vec4 in_COLOR0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TEXCOORD3;

out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_COLOR0;
out highp vec3 vs_NORMAL0;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD4;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
mediump float u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;

float u_xlat4;
bool u_xlatb4;
vec2 u_xlat5;
vec3 u_xlat6;

bool u_xlatb6;
mediump float u_xlat16_7;
vec2 u_xlat9;
bool u_xlatb10;
